NK068(nyu)001:10197: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK068(nyu)001:10199: gnyis pa cig car ba'i 'bras bu ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10200: dkyil 'khor kun tu sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10201: bsgrub bya'i tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor kun dang lam du
NK068(nyu)001:10202: gyur pa'i 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi'i char gtogs pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10203: ye shes chig chod du rang rig la gsal ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:10204: blos rab tu sbyor bas na rang bzhin 'bras bu
NK068(nyu)001:10205: mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi che ba'i yon tan
NK068(nyu)001:10207: de ltar yang ma ning gi rgyud las /
NK068(nyu)001:10209: byang chub sems las ma yengs na //
NK068(nyu)001:10210: dkyil 'khor snying po lhun grub pas //
NK068(nyu)001:10211: thams cad dus gcig bsgom par 'gyur //
NK068(nyu)001:10218: de skad ces ston pas 'khor gyi ched du brjod
NK068(nyu)001:10219: pas sems nyid gzhi ma nges pas snang spyod thams
NK068(nyu)001:10220: cad ye shes kyi rol mor 'char ba'i sprin gyis
NK068(nyu)001:10224: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:10225: 'dis tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i sgo nas tshogs
NK068(nyu)001:10226: kyi 'bras bu sgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o
NK068(nyu)001:10228: // // da ni le'u bcu gsum pa 'chad par byed pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:10229: chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na /
NK068(nyu)001:10230: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gsum ka ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10231: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10232: mtshan nyid gsum las gsum ka ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10233: lam la thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10234: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa gtso cher ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10235: 'bring gi chos lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10236: de la bcu las gzhung hril pos byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10237: de'i zhor la lta ba ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10239: ting nge 'dzin dang phrin las zur tsam ston /
NK068(nyu)001:10240: tha ma'i chos bcu las rang bzhin lta ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10243: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK068(nyu)001:10244: de ltar ston pa'i le'u 'di la gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10250: tshogs sgrub pa'i tshul dang 'bras bu bstan pa de
NK068(nyu)001:10251: nas thabs grol gyi man ngag zab pa rnams ston
NK068(nyu)001:10252: pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa phyogs bcu dus bzhis
NK068(nyu)001:10253: bsdus pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs dbyer mi
NK068(nyu)001:10254: phyed pa'i rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor thams cad rig pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10255: ye shes rang snang ba las tha mi dad pas
NK068(nyu)001:10256: gcig tu 'dus nas gnas pa'i ston pa bcom ldan
NK068(nyu)001:10257: 'das dgyes pa chen pos srid zhi'i chos thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:10258: ye nas rdzogs pa chen po rang byung gi ye
NK068(nyu)001:10259: shes su ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa las mi
NK068(nyu)001:10260: 'da' ba'i dam tshig snod min la shin tu gsang
NK068(nyu)001:10261: ba'i rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po de kho na
NK068(nyu)001:10262: nyid mtshon par byed pa'i sgo /
NK068(nyu)001:10263: myong bar byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10264: rtogs par byed pa'i 'bras bu la sogs pa'i sprin
NK068(nyu)001:10265: rnam par bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK068(nyu)001:10266: zhugs nas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK068(nyu)001:10267: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10271: man ngag gi ngo bo bshad pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10272: de gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba bshad pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10273: yul gang la gdams pa'i snod bshad pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10282: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba mtshon pa'i sgo /
NK068(nyu)001:10283: de gnyis ka'i tha snyad mtshon byed skyi sgo /
NK068(nyu)001:10284: mtshan bya don gyi khyad par 'byin tshul lo //
NK068(nyu)001:10286: ma rtogs pa dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10288: dang po 'jig rten pa'i lta ba la ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs pa gnyis kyi /
NK068(nyu)001:10289: ma rtogs pa ni 'jig rten phal pa ste ma
NK068(nyu)001:10290: rig pa dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i sor bzhag lha
NK068(nyu)001:10291: dang mi'i theg pa gnyis po zhes bzhed pa'ang yod
NK068(nyu)001:10292: mod kyi / 'dir man ngag lta phreng dang bi
NK068(nyu)001:10293: ma la'i 'grel chung las phyal rgyang gnyis la bzhed
NK068(nyu)001:10295: de yang skye bo de rnams las rgyu 'bras dang
NK068(nyu)001:10296: tshe snga phyi la sogs pa yod par yang ma
NK068(nyu)001:10297: rtogs / med par yang ma rtogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:10298: de gnyis gang la'ang blo rten mi 'cha' bar kun tu rmongs pa rnams ni phyal ba zhes bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10299: tshe snga phyi dang las rgyu 'bral yod pa tsam
NK068(nyu)001:10300: rtogs kyang phyi ma rgyab tu bor nas tshe 'di'i
NK068(nyu)001:10301: btsan phyug sogs bsgrub pa ni rgyang 'phen zhes bya'o
NK068(nyu)001:10302: // de la phyal ba ni ma rtogs pa dngos dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10303: rgyang 'phen pa ni zhar las byung ba'i ma rtogs pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10304: de gnyis ka grub mthas blo bsgyur ba'i lta ba
NK068(nyu)001:10305: ma yin kyang sems kyi gnas tshul bsdu ba'i phyir
NK068(nyu)001:10307: gnyis pa log par rtogs pa la gnyis /
NK068(nyu)001:10308: chad lta mur stug pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10311: chos nyid cir yang ma grub pas 'khrul gzhi byas
NK068(nyu)001:10312: nas las rgyu 'bras tshe snga phyi med par lta
NK068(nyu)001:10313: ba ste / tshe gcig gi chos thams cad rgyu
NK068(nyu)001:10314: med glo bur du skye zhing mtha' chad par smra
NK068(nyu)001:10315: bas snga phyi'i mur thug pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10317: mdzes ma zhim par g.yos la ci dgar spyod //
NK068(nyu)001:10318: shi nas de yi spyod yul min //
NK068(nyu)001:10319: me shi thal ba rlung khyer ltar //
NK068(nyu)001:10320: slar skye ba dag ga la yod //
NK068(nyu)001:10321: gang zhig rgyu 'bras yod smra ba //
NK068(nyu)001:10322: yi dwags spyang ka'i rjes dang mtshungs //
NK068(nyu)001:10325: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pas 'khrul gzhi byas nas
NK068(nyu)001:10326: bdag dang dbang phyug la sogs pa rtag pa gcig
NK068(nyu)001:10327: pu bde ba rang dbang can du 'dod pa ste
NK068(nyu)001:10331: gcer pu pa dang bzhi'i steng du chad lta mur
NK068(nyu)001:10332: stug pa bsnan pas ta rka sde lnga zhes grags
NK068(nyu)001:10333: shing / de thams cad bdag tu lta ba mthun te /
NK068(nyu)001:10334: bzhi pos bdag rtag par 'dod la /
NK068(nyu)001:10335: mur stug pa ni bdag yod pa chad par 'dod pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10336: rgyu mtshan des na 'di rnams 'khor ba las grol ba'i thabs ma yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:10337: 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bdag 'dzin gyis bcings pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:10338: de ltar yang 'grel pa spar khab las /
NK068(nyu)001:10339: de la rtag chad gnyis ni log par rtogs pa ste phyogs las gol ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10341: gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba la rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis las /
NK068(nyu)001:10342: dang po rgyu'i theg pa la'ang /
NK068(nyu)001:10343: rnam par thar pa'i sgo phyogs re tsam du rtogs pa ni nyan thos dang rang rgyal gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10344: de yang nyan thos pas chos bdag gzung yul rdul
NK068(nyu)001:10345: phra rab dang 'dzin sems skad cig ma don dam
NK068(nyu)001:10346: du 'dod cing / gang zag gi bdag gzung yul
NK068(nyu)001:10347: rags pa dang 'dzin sems rgyun dang bcas pa kun
NK068(nyu)001:10348: rdzob tsam du snang ba las rang bzhin med par
NK068(nyu)001:10349: du 'dod cing / rtogs pa'o // de la dbye
NK068(nyu)001:10350: na bye brag smra ba ni 'di ltar snang ba
NK068(nyu)001:10351: sgo lnga'i yul rnams phyi rol gyi don du bden
NK068(nyu)001:10353: mdo sde pa ni 'di ltar snang ba ni 'dzin
NK068(nyu)001:10354: sems kyi rnam par myong ba yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:10355: de'i lkog na de dang rigs 'dra'i don bden rdzas grub gcig yod par 'dod do //
NK068(nyu)001:10356: rang rgyal ni gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa nyan thos dang mthun la /
NK068(nyu)001:10357: de'i steng du chos bdag gi gzung cha rdul phra rab kyang rang bzhin med par rtogs pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10358: 'dir phyi pa mu stegs pa dang nang pa sangs rgyas kyi khyad par ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10359: lta ba gang zag gi bdag 'dod cing rtag gcig
NK068(nyu)001:10360: bde ba rang dbang can dngos por smra ba ba'am
NK068(nyu)001:10361: / yang na las rgyu 'bras dang tshe snga phyi med par lta ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10362: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su mi 'gro zhing /
NK068(nyu)001:10363: chos rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi khas mi len pa ni phyi pa mu stegs pa yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:10364: de las ldog pa nang pa sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10365: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam thar gyi sgo la
NK068(nyu)001:10366: spyod kyang rdo rje theg pa'i don ma mthong bas
NK068(nyu)001:10367: yang dag nyid ma rtogs pa ni theg chen dbu
NK068(nyu)001:10368: sems gnyis te / sems tsam pas don dam par
NK068(nyu)001:10369: gzung 'dzin gnyis med dam rnam gcod bkag nas yongs
NK068(nyu)001:10371: de la dbye na rnam bden pa ni snang ba
NK068(nyu)001:10372: thams cad don du mi bden kyang shes ngor bden
NK068(nyu)001:10373: par 'dod / de'i nang nas kyang rnam rig pa
NK068(nyu)001:10374: dang don sems gnyis ni yin pa gcig yin pa
NK068(nyu)001:10375: par 'dod / / yod pa tha dad du yod pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10376: rnam pa mtshungs pa ste rnam rig gnyis sgo nga bkas pa ltar du 'dod /
NK068(nyu)001:10377: rnam rdzun pas rnam pa ni sems kyis sgro btags
NK068(nyu)001:10378: pa'i sgro btags tsam snang ba yin pa'i phyir bden
NK068(nyu)001:10380: dbu ma pa ni rnam gcod bkag nas yongs gcod spros bral las khas mi len pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10381: de yang dbu ma rang rgyud pa ni yang dag
NK068(nyu)001:10382: pa'i kun rdzob dang log pa'i kun rdzob khyad par
NK068(nyu)001:10383: 'byed la / thal 'gyur ba ni rang phyogs bsgrub
NK068(nyu)001:10384: rgyu med pa ltar gzhan phyogs dgag tu med de
NK068(nyu)001:10385: yang log khyad par med par 'dod do //
NK068(nyu)001:10386: 'dir theg pa che chung gi khyad par ni shes rab dang snying rjes dbye ba ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10387: shes rab chung bas bdag med gnyis ka rtogs ma nus /
NK068(nyu)001:10388: snying rje chung bas gzhan don spyod par mi nus pa ni theg pa chung ngu'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10389: de las ldog pa ni theg chen te /
NK068(nyu)001:10391: theg pa'i khyad par shes rab snying rjes te //
NK068(nyu)001:10392: de min theg pa chen por khas 'ches pas //
NK068(nyu)001:10393: bong bus seng ge'i lpags pa gyon dang mtshungs //
NK068(nyu)001:10395: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i theg pa la phyi nang gnyis las /
NK068(nyu)001:10396: dang po phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:10397: sgo gsum gyi bya bas rgyud 'dul ba gtso bor ston pa kri ya dang u pa ya /
NK068(nyu)001:10398: sems kyi dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gtso bor byed pas 'bras bu bsgrub pa ni yo ga'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10399: 'dir rgyud mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa'i khyad par ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10400: sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyu ru 'dod cing don
NK068(nyu)001:10401: dam bsgrub byar byas nas kun rdzob spang byar byed
NK068(nyu)001:10402: pa ni mtshan nyid kyi theg pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10403: sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bur 'dod cing kun
NK068(nyu)001:10404: rdzob kyang mi spong bar lam du byed pa ni
NK068(nyu)001:10406: gnyis pa nang pa thabs kyi rgyud la /
NK068(nyu)001:10407: phyi rgyud man chad thun mong pa'i yul du ma
NK068(nyu)001:10408: gyur pas chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong bden
NK068(nyu)001:10409: gnyis dbyer med kyi zin te cho ga yan lag
NK068(nyu)001:10410: gi lha bskyed pa'i phyir spyod pa gtso bor byed
NK068(nyu)001:10411: pa gsang ba pha rgyud bskyed pa ma h+aa yo
NK068(nyu)001:10412: ga dang / chos thams cad sems dbyings dang ye
NK068(nyu)001:10413: shes gnyis su med par rtogs pas ma h+aa'i bskyed
NK068(nyu)001:10414: rim la mi brten par chu las nya ldang ba
NK068(nyu)001:10415: ltar rdzogs pa ting nge 'dzin la gtso bor byed
NK068(nyu)001:10416: pa ma rgyud rdzogs pa a nu yo ga'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10417: chos thams cad ye nas skye 'gags rang bzhin gyis
NK068(nyu)001:10418: rnam par dag pa rang byung gi ye shes su
NK068(nyu)001:10419: gnas pa'i don rtogs shing 'og ma gnyis ltar bskyed
NK068(nyu)001:10420: du med pa'i phyir rtsol ba las grol ba ni
NK068(nyu)001:10421: a nu man chad kyi yul du ma gyur pas
NK068(nyu)001:10422: gsang ba gnyis med kyi rgyud lta ba gtso bor
NK068(nyu)001:10423: byed pa a ti yo ga ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10424: de ltar ma h+aa yo ga la gsum du phye bas bskyed rdzogs gsum mo //
NK068(nyu)001:10426: gzhung 'di ma h+aa'i theg pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:10427: gong ma gnyis kyi lta ba gtan la 'bebs pa mi 'thad de /
NK068(nyu)001:10428: 'og mas gong ma'i don mi mthong ba'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:10429: man ngag lta phreng gi dgongs pa bzhin rnal 'byor
NK068(nyu)001:10430: chen po'i tshul yang gsum du phye bas 'di ma
NK068(nyu)001:10431: h+aa'i a nu dang a ti yin pa'i phyir 'di
NK068(nyu)001:10433: 'dir sngags kyi phyi nang gi khyad par gang zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:10434: lta spyod ting nge 'dzin gsum dbyer med du 'dod pa sngags nang pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10436: 'o na sngags phyi pa dang mtshan nyid theg pa la khyad par med dam zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:10438: kun rdzob lam du byed nus mi nus kyi khyad par ro //
NK068(nyu)001:10439: de ltar a ti man chad kyi don de rnams ni mtshon byed sgo'i khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10441: yi ge sgra btags sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10442: mtshon bya de rnams tha snyad gang gis mtshon zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:10443: yi ge a las sgra'i nga ro dang ming gzhi
NK068(nyu)001:10444: gsal bar byed pa'i tha snyad kyis btags pa dbyangs
NK068(nyu)001:10446: gsal byed so bzhi sogs yi ge sil bu 'dus
NK068(nyu)001:10447: pa las don gyi ngo bo tsam ston pa'i ming
NK068(nyu)001:10448: 'byung zhing / de du ma tshogs pa la brten
NK068(nyu)001:10449: nas don gyi khyad par gsal bar byed pa'i tshig
NK068(nyu)001:10450: dang tshig gi tshogs mang du 'dus pa las gzhung
NK068(nyu)001:10452: des rang rang gi brjod bya'i don rab tu mtshon te /
NK068(nyu)001:10453: bstan pa dang theg pa du mar snang ba ni mtshon par byed pa'i sgo zhes bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10455: khong nas sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10456: spyir gzhung tshig so so'i khong nas rang rang gi brjod bya'i don ma 'dres par gnas shing /
NK068(nyu)001:10457: khyad par mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud sems can
NK068(nyu)001:10458: gyi khong na gnas kyang rtogs dka' bas gab cing
NK068(nyu)001:10459: / mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud du gsang
NK068(nyu)001:10460: ba zam mo rnam skal med kyi mi go ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:10462: de ltar gab sbas kyi don gnyis po de 'byin
NK068(nyu)001:10463: par byed pa po ni rgyud don phyin ci ma
NK068(nyu)001:10464: log par ston pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi thugs
NK068(nyu)001:10465: la gnas pa'i phyir des 'byin par byed do //
NK068(nyu)001:10467: ston pa kun tu bzang po'i thugs la gab cing
NK068(nyu)001:10468: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyi nang du sbas pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10469: don 'di dag rgyal rnams dgongs pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10471: gang zag rnams snyan khung du brgyud nas rdo rje
NK068(nyu)001:10472: 'dzin pa'i slob dpon gyis rgyud kyi don rnams dkrugs
NK068(nyu)001:10473: pa bsdebs gcus pa bsrang gab pa mngon du phyung
NK068(nyu)001:10476: gzu lum can dang ras chod can la gab cing
NK068(nyu)001:10477: sbas pa'i don de dag snod dang ldan pa'i slob
NK068(nyu)001:10478: bu la bla ma brgyud pa'i man ngag gis rgyud
NK068(nyu)001:10479: kyi don phyin ci ma log par rtogs shing khong
NK068(nyu)001:10481: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir na spyir gsang sngags rdo rje'i
NK068(nyu)001:10482: theg pa sgos rgyud gzhung 'di nyid yang sgos su
NK068(nyu)001:10483: le'u bcu gsum pa 'di yang chig brgyud dang don
NK068(nyu)001:10484: brgyud dang snyan brgyud gsum 'dzom la bar ma chad
NK068(nyu)001:10485: pa'i rdo rje'i slob dpon la rag las par shes
NK068(nyu)001:10486: par bya'o // gnyis pa myong bar byed pa'i thabs la /
NK068(nyu)001:10487: gzhung 'di'i steng du sngon gyi bshad srol rnying pa
NK068(nyu)001:10488: la bskyed pa'i rim pa'i dbang du bstan pa dang
NK068(nyu)001:10489: / rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i dbang du bstan pa'i bshad lugs gnyis gsungs /
NK068(nyu)001:10490: 'grel pa spar khab nas phyi bskyed rim /
NK068(nyu)001:10492: gsang ba rdzogs pa'i rdzogs rim dang bshad lugs gsum du gsungs /
NK068(nyu)001:10493: 'grel chung las dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis dang sbyar ba'i bshad lugs gcig gsungs /
NK068(nyu)001:10494: rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed pa la sgyu 'phrul lam
NK068(nyu)001:10495: rim gyis rgyab byas nas grol lam rim gyis pa
NK068(nyu)001:10497: man ngag lta phreng gis rgyab byas nas grol lam cig car ba ltar du bshad pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10498: thabs lam rim gyis pa steng sgo ltar bshad pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10499: thabs lam cig car ba 'og sgo ltar bshad pa dang bshad lugs bzhi ru 'thad gsungs shing /
NK068(nyu)001:10500: 'brel ba mkhan gyi phyag len la bshad lugs gsum du mdzad kyang /
NK068(nyu)001:10501: 'dir gsang bdag sgro phug pa'i rjes su 'brang nas gzhung gcig gi steng du bshad tshul gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10502: shes rab grol lam gyi dbang du bshad pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10503: thabs lam gdams ngag gi dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10505: grol lam rim gyis pa ltar du bshad pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10506: grol lam cig car ba ltar du bshad pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10507: dang po la'ang mtshan nyid gsum las /
NK068(nyu)001:10508: dang po rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10510: zhes te rang rig pa ye nas rang bzhin gyis
NK068(nyu)001:10511: rnam par dag pa dang rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:10512: 'khor lhag pa bden pa dbyer med chos sku chen
NK068(nyu)001:10513: po blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba des 'khor 'das
NK068(nyu)001:10514: kyi chos thams cad la ris med du ldan par
NK068(nyu)001:10515: khyab pa ni lta ba'i ngo bo ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10516: de lta bu'i gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:10517: lnga'i rang bzhin can de nyid rtogs pa bzhi dang
NK068(nyu)001:10518: dag pa gsum dang mnyam pa gnyis kyi gtan tshigs
NK068(nyu)001:10519: rnams kyis gtan la phab pas yul med rang gsal
NK068(nyu)001:10520: du rtog pa ni grub mtha'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10521: de yang ldan pa'am khyab pa'i don ni rten dang
NK068(nyu)001:10522: brten pa lta bu ma yin te rang bzhin ngo
NK068(nyu)001:10524: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10525: dkyil 'khor la ni sogs tshigs bcad phyed dang bzhi ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10526: ye nas rnam par dag pa chos nyid don gyi
NK068(nyu)001:10527: dkyil 'khor de la ni rnam par rtog pa'i ting
NK068(nyu)001:10528: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus
NK068(nyu)001:10529: pa'i chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa ye
NK068(nyu)001:10530: shes lnga'i don dang ldan par bsgom pa ni de
NK068(nyu)001:10531: bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK068(nyu)001:10532: don dam spros bral gyi dkyil 'khor de lta bu
NK068(nyu)001:10533: yin kyang kun rdzob sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor snying rje
NK068(nyu)001:10534: chen po nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsgom pa las
NK068(nyu)001:10535: byung ba ni kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK068(nyu)001:10536: no // de ltar stong pa dang snying rje'i rgya
NK068(nyu)001:10537: mi 'bral ba'i phyir phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor
NK068(nyu)001:10538: bsgom pa la phra rags gnyis las /
NK068(nyu)001:10539: dang po phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa'i skabs
NK068(nyu)001:10540: su de gnyis zung du 'jug pa mi 'gyur ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:10541: bde ba chen po cir yang ma 'gags pa las
NK068(nyu)001:10542: rang byung ba'i yi ger ar snang ba ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10543: de las a phra mo dang ka sogs kyi 'phro 'du la sems sbyang zhing /
NK068(nyu)001:10544: de thams cad kyang thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:10545: kyi ngo bo yi ge h+aum gi dkyil 'khor du
NK068(nyu)001:10546: bsdus te gsal bar bsgom pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10547: gnyis pa rags pa lha sku la bslab pa'i skabs
NK068(nyu)001:10548: su gsung yig 'bru de yongs su gyur pa las
NK068(nyu)001:10549: thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK068(nyu)001:10550: de yang yongs su gyur pa las rtsa ba'i lha
NK068(nyu)001:10551: rdo rje sems dpa' sku'i dkyil 'khor la ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:10552: sems dpa' sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum dbu rgyan
NK068(nyu)001:10553: rigs kyi lha lngas bskor ba ste yan lag pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10554: lha dgu dang bcas pa yongs su rdzogs pa dbyer
NK068(nyu)001:10555: med pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10556: de ltar phra rags gnyis po de ni phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK068(nyu)001:10557: des dkyil 'khor thams cad sgom par 'gyur bas na mchog yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:10558: de ltar stong pa dang snying rje gnyis su med
NK068(nyu)001:10559: pa'i lha'i sku snang la rang bzhin med pa de
NK068(nyu)001:10560: nyid phal gyis rtogs par dka' zhing gcig tu zlum
NK068(nyu)001:10561: pas na gsang ba'i thig le ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10562: de ka dkyil 'khor gyi lha du ma'i 'byung khungs su gyur pas na dbyings so //
NK068(nyu)001:10563: yang na phyag rgya spros bcas kyi skabs su rtog
NK068(nyu)001:10564: tshogs du mar lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du
NK068(nyu)001:10565: gnas pa'i don rtogs dka' bas na gsang ba'i don
NK068(nyu)001:10566: yin la lha du ma'ang lha gcig tu zlum pas
NK068(nyu)001:10567: na thig le / rang rig pa'i dkyil 'khor de
NK068(nyu)001:10568: lha du ma'i 'byung khungs su gyur pas na dbyings
NK068(nyu)001:10569: na thig le / zhes bya'o // de yang 'byung
NK068(nyu)001:10570: ba lnga ni cha phra ba shes rab ste rigs
NK068(nyu)001:10572: chen po phung po ni rags pa thabs te rigs
NK068(nyu)001:10573: kyi de bzhin gshegs pa yab lngar bsgom pa nyid
NK068(nyu)001:10574: do // gzhan yang dbang po bzhi dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10577: reg pa ste rnam par shes pa bzhi dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10578: shugs las gsang ba'i dbang po dang yul dang rnam shes te gsum 'dus kyi reg pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10579: phyin ci log bzhi rnams kyi rtog pa ni byang
NK068(nyu)001:10580: chub sems dpa' dang sems ma dang khro bo dang
NK068(nyu)001:10581: khro mo rnams su gsal ba yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:10582: de ltar lha dang rtog pa dbyer mi phyed pa ni rdo rje'i tshogs zhes bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10583: de bzhin yid dang chos kyi rtog pa'i spyod yul
NK068(nyu)001:10584: yongs su dag pas na kun tu bzang po dang
NK068(nyu)001:10585: bzang mo thub pa drug dang bcas ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK068(nyu)001:10586: gyi lha tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po ni rtsa
NK068(nyu)001:10588: de ltar rtsa ba'i la re re la'ang yab la yab nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10589: yum la yum bco brgyad bkod pa ni thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:10590: de ltar thabs lha bzhi bcu po'i thugs kar chos
NK068(nyu)001:10591: thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen po rang byung gi
NK068(nyu)001:10592: ye shes mtshon pa'i rtags su ye shes sems dpa'
NK068(nyu)001:10593: re re bsgom pa ni shes rab kyi lha bzhi
NK068(nyu)001:10594: bcu'o // thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu po re re
NK068(nyu)001:10595: la yang lhag pa'i lha sku gsung thugs kyi gnas
NK068(nyu)001:10596: su rnam snang dang mtha' yas dang mi bskyod pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10597: cha lugs can re re bsgom mo //
NK068(nyu)001:10598: de ltar bzhi bcu po tshan bzhi po la yang
NK068(nyu)001:10599: thugs rig pa rang byung ye shes kyi snang cha
NK068(nyu)001:10600: ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i dbu rgyan gyi lha lngar
NK068(nyu)001:10601: lta zhing / de ltar rtsa ba'i lha yan lag
NK068(nyu)001:10602: lhag pa'i lha dang bcas pa nyi khri bzhi stong
NK068(nyu)001:10603: po thams cad gsal ba yul gyis mi 'phrog par
NK068(nyu)001:10604: bsgom pa ni snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting
NK068(nyu)001:10605: nge 'dzin zhes bya ste phyag rgya spros bcas so
NK068(nyu)001:10606: lta zhing / // dwangs ma dkar dmar gyi snying
NK068(nyu)001:10607: po'i thig le dbab ldog gi sbyor bas lhan skyes
NK068(nyu)001:10608: kyi ye shes la mnyam par sbyor ba ni +aa
NK068(nyu)001:10609: lta zhing / // li ste / des mtshon nas
NK068(nyu)001:10610: yo byad lnga po rnams yul dang yul can gnyis
NK068(nyu)001:10611: su med par mnyam par sbyor bas spyod bzhin ma
NK068(nyu)001:10612: chags pa bde ba'i ye shes kyi rol mo yis
NK068(nyu)001:10613: lta zhing / // li ste / / rtog tshogs
NK068(nyu)001:10614: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang gsal bas dgyes
NK068(nyu)001:10615: pa dang ldan pa'i lha nyid la nyid rol pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10616: tshul du mchod pa mnyam rdzogs chen por dbul ba
NK068(nyu)001:10617: ni tshom bu tshogs sgrub bo //
NK068(nyu)001:10618: gsum pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10619: zag pa sogs rkang pa dgu ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10620: de yang tshogs sgrub kyi dus kyi yo byad lnga
NK068(nyu)001:10621: po rnams la 'dzin pa bral bas na zag pa
NK068(nyu)001:10622: med pa'i phyir ye shes kyi tshogs dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10623: ma 'gags par spyod pa bsod nams kyi tshogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:10624: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i nus mthu las 'byung ba'i gnas
NK068(nyu)001:10625: skabs kyi 'bras bu mthong lam rig 'dzin rnam smin
NK068(nyu)001:10626: dang tshe dbang gnyis gang rung zhig thob cing /
NK068(nyu)001:10627: de nas bsgom lam phyag chen dang mthar lam lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro //
NK068(nyu)001:10628: lhun grub rig 'dzin de'i cha lugs ni ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:10629: sgyu ma sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i cha lugs
NK068(nyu)001:10630: dang mthun par rang snang ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10631: sems nyid gzhi ma nges pa las 'bras bu sna tshogs snang bas na rol mo ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10632: lhun grub rig 'dzin de'i mnyam par bzhag dus kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10633: dgongs pa ni snang grags thams cad lha dang lha
NK068(nyu)001:10635: yon tan mtha' yas pa dang ldan pas na zag bcas kyi lam las mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10636: gang gis tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i nus mthu las byung
NK068(nyu)001:10637: ba'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu rang bzhin nyid kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10638: dkyil 'khor snang stong dbyer mi phyed pa ni de
NK068(nyu)001:10639: ni phal pas yul min cing spros pa dang bral
NK068(nyu)001:10640: bas na gsang ba'i thig le zhes bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10641: de nyid kyi don mtshan nyid gsum gyi mngon du
NK068(nyu)001:10642: byas pa ni dbyings rnam par dag pa zung 'jug
NK068(nyu)001:10644: rnam par dag pa'i chos sku de ni dus gsum
NK068(nyu)001:10645: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhi'i ngo bo yin te
NK068(nyu)001:10646: / chos kyi sku de thob tshe de'i yon tan
NK068(nyu)001:10647: gyi cha la sku lnga lhun gyis grub pas phyogs
NK068(nyu)001:10648: bcu dang dus bzhi'i rgyal ba thams cad kyang mngon
NK068(nyu)001:10650: de ltar rgyal ba thams cad kyi sku lnga gsung
NK068(nyu)001:10651: lnga yon tan lnga phrin las lnga thugs lnga ste
NK068(nyu)001:10652: nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa ma lus pa
NK068(nyu)001:10653: thob pa ni bdag nyid kyi zhal bdag nyid kyis
NK068(nyu)001:10655: de ltar 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gnyis su
NK068(nyu)001:10656: med pa'i bdag nyid du rang dbang bsgyur ba'i mchog
NK068(nyu)001:10657: nyid de / slob lam gyi rtse mor phyin pas lam gyi nang nas dam pa yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:10658: de ltar man ngag lam rim gyis rgyab byas nas
NK068(nyu)001:10659: grol lam rim gyis pa ltar du bshad pa ste
NK068(nyu)001:10660: / 'di la snga rabs pa rnams kyis bskyed rim zhes bshad na'ang /
NK068(nyu)001:10661: grol lam cig car ba la ltos nas de ltar gsungs pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:10662: rim gnyis kyi zlas phye ba'i bskyed rim ni min te /
NK068(nyu)001:10663: gal te yin na de kho na la bslab pas
NK068(nyu)001:10664: spyod pa'i nye rgyu tshogs sgrub kyis zag med mthong
NK068(nyu)001:10665: lam la sbyor ba mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:10666: des lam rim du phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su
NK068(nyu)001:10667: cho ga gsum bskyed dang bzlas pa bya tshul sogs
NK068(nyu)001:10668: 'byung yang de tsam gyis bskyed rim kho nar mi
NK068(nyu)001:10669: 'gyur te / rdzogs rim gyis drangs pa'i lha'i gsal
NK068(nyu)001:10670: snang la bslab tshul dang thun mtshams kyi bya ba
NK068(nyu)001:10672: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu bslab pa'i ched du gsungs so //
NK068(nyu)001:10673: 'on kyang bskyed rim ltar bslab pa'ang mtha' gcig tu ni mi 'gog ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10674: gang zag 'ga' zhig bskyed rim lha'i gsal snang ci rigs thob nas /
NK068(nyu)001:10675: tshogs kyi spyod pas thun mong gi dngos grub mkha'
NK068(nyu)001:10676: spyod sgrub te dngos dang sprul pa'i sgo nas sems
NK068(nyu)001:10678: rten des rgyal ba rnams mnyes par byas pa'i mthus
NK068(nyu)001:10679: rdzogs rim la zhugs te zung 'jug gi sku sgrub
NK068(nyu)001:10680: pa ni yod par 'dod dgos so //
NK068(nyu)001:10681: gnyis pa cig car ba ltar bshad pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:10684: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10685: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas
NK068(nyu)001:10686: te rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa yin gyi
NK068(nyu)001:10687: / phyis lam gyis 'bras bu gsar du bsgrubs pa ni ma yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:10688: chos rnams kyi rang bzhin de ltar yin kyang yin
NK068(nyu)001:10689: pa tsam gyis phan mi thogs pas gzhi de ltar
NK068(nyu)001:10690: yin pa lam gyis mngon du rtogs par bya dgos
NK068(nyu)001:10691: te / de yang dkyil 'khor sems can thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:10692: la ye nas rang chas su ldan pa'i don rtogs
NK068(nyu)001:10693: nas ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyis ye nas
NK068(nyu)001:10694: yin pa'i dkyil 'khor de la ni de ltar yin
NK068(nyu)001:10695: tshul shes pas dkyil 'khor du gsal 'debs shing bsgom
NK068(nyu)001:10696: par byas nas rang bzhin dkyil 'khor dang mnyam par
NK068(nyu)001:10697: sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor las byung
NK068(nyu)001:10698: ba ni thugs rig pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK068(nyu)001:10699: te / zhes bya ste / dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi mchog 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK068(nyu)001:10701: dang po dkyil 'khor ji ltar ldan par bstan pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10702: 'byung ba sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10703: 'byung ba lnga cha phra ba ni shes rab rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK068(nyu)001:10704: chen po 'byung ba rags pa ste phung po lnga
NK068(nyu)001:10705: rigs kyi yab lnga yin pa de bzhin du mig
NK068(nyu)001:10709: reg pa ni mig sogs rnam shes bzhi rnams byang sems yab yum dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10710: gsang ba'i dbang po'i yul rnam shes gsum 'dus kyi rig pa dang bzhi ni sgo ba bzhi /
NK068(nyu)001:10711: rtag chad mu bzhi sgo ma bzhi /
NK068(nyu)001:10712: yid chos kun bzang yab yum /
NK068(nyu)001:10713: nyon mongs pa drug thub pa drug ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10714: rtog pa dang lha de dag rdo rje'i tshogs dbyer med pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10715: 'gro ba kun la de ltar ye nas rang chas su ldan pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10716: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar bsgom tshul ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10717: kun tu bzang po'i sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10718: de ltar 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye nas
NK068(nyu)001:10719: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas pa
NK068(nyu)001:10720: de la / de'i don legs par rtogs pa'i rnal
NK068(nyu)001:10721: 'byor pa bdag nyid chen pos ye nas yod pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10722: lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med dgongs pa zab mo
NK068(nyu)001:10723: de la / ste / thugs rang byung gi ye
NK068(nyu)001:10724: shes spros pa'i mtha' dang bral ba las rol pa
NK068(nyu)001:10725: cir yang snang ba ye shes lngar 'char ba'i tshul
NK068(nyu)001:10726: gyis lta zhing bsgom par bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10727: gsum pa de ltar bsgom pa las cir 'gyur ba ni /
NK068(nyu)001:10728: snying po'i sogs tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10729: chos thams cad kyi snying po thig le nyag cig
NK068(nyu)001:10730: dang gnyis su med par mnyam par sbyor ba las
NK068(nyu)001:10731: rig pa rang byung bde ba chen po'i ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:10732: de nyid kyi rol mo sna tshogs par 'char ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:10733: sprin gyis ye shes la ye shes dgyes par rol
NK068(nyu)001:10734: pa'i tshul du mchod pa dbul zhes bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10735: de ltar snang tshul sna tshogs yod kyang rtsa ba
NK068(nyu)001:10736: gnas lugs las ma g.yos pa ste zag pa med
NK068(nyu)001:10737: pa'i bsod nams kyi stobs kyis bsgrubs pa'i ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:10738: sgyu ma lta bur ma 'gag par rang snang ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:10739: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor rnam 'gyur mtha' yas par 'khrul
NK068(nyu)001:10740: yang mchog tu gsang ba'i thig le gnas lugs de
NK068(nyu)001:10741: bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las cung zad tsam gzhan du
NK068(nyu)001:10743: de lta bu'i man ngag dang man ngag can gyi yon tan gang zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:10744: gnas lugs de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhi
NK068(nyu)001:10745: ste thugs kyi brnag pa'i man ngag gi don yin
NK068(nyu)001:10746: la / de lta bu'i man ngag dang ldan pa
NK068(nyu)001:10747: ni phyogs bcu dus bzhir tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK068(nyu)001:10748: rgyas ma lus pa thams cad bdag nyid kyi ye
NK068(nyu)001:10749: shes las mi gzhan pa'i tshul du sku'i zhal mthong
NK068(nyu)001:10750: la / ba dang / gsung chos la dbang bsgyur ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10751: yon tan phrin las mthar phyin pa'i mchog nyid dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10752: thugs dbyer mi phyed pas bslu ba nam yang med pa'i skyabs kyi dam par gyur pa yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:10753: man ngag gi gnad 'di ni slob dpon pad+mas lta ba'i phreng bar /
NK068(nyu)001:10754: rtogs pa bzhi'i lam gyis yid ches par bya ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10755: mtshan nyid gsum gyis don mthar dbyung ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10756: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis don lhun gyis grub par bya ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10757: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i thabs bstan pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10758: don rnam pa bzhir phye nas gsungs pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:10759: phyi ma ni 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur zhing /
NK068(nyu)001:10760: dang po gsum ni sngar bshad pa'i gnad du 'dus par gsungs so //
NK068(nyu)001:10761: gnyis pa thabs lam gdams ngag gi dbang du bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10762: steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag ltar bshad pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10763: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag ltar bshad pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10768: khyab brdal chen po'i man ngag go //
NK068(nyu)001:10770: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10771: de yang tsit+ta smug po gur phub pa 'dra ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:10772: dbus su rtsa'i dwangs ma brgyad yod pa rtsa bzhir
NK068(nyu)001:10773: 'du ste / mdun gyi gsum chos nyid kyii rtsa
NK068(nyu)001:10774: ste skye ba med par rang snang ba'i las byed
NK068(nyu)001:10775: 'du ste / pa / g.yas kyi rtsa gcig ye
NK068(nyu)001:10776: shes kyi rtsa ste ye shes nyer lnga sogs 'char
NK068(nyu)001:10778: g.yon gyi rtsa gcig yon tan gyi rtsa ste mngon
NK068(nyu)001:10779: shes dang 'bras bu'i chos rnams snang ba'i las byed
NK068(nyu)001:10780: pa / rgyab kyi rtsa gsum rang rgyud kyi rtsa
NK068(nyu)001:10781: ste shes pa rnams rmongs shing 'joms pa'i las byed
NK068(nyu)001:10782: pa / do // rtsa de dag gi sbubs 'od bzhi dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10783: de'ikhroda na sbyang bya dang sbyong byed kyi sa bon rnam shes dang bcas pa rnams gnas te /
NK068(nyu)001:10784: chos nyid kyi rtsa la 'od zlum po dkar po /
NK068(nyu)001:10788: ye shes kyi rtsa la 'od gru bzhi ser po /
NK068(nyu)001:10792: yon tan gyi rtsa la 'od zla gam dmar po /
NK068(nyu)001:10794: sbyong byed +aah nyon mongs pa can gyi yid /
NK068(nyu)001:10795: rang rgyud kyi rtsa la 'od gru gsum dmar nag /
NK068(nyu)001:10796: sbyang bya dang sbyong byed kyi yig 'bru ni med do //
NK068(nyu)001:10797: sgo lnga'i rnam shes gnyid dang bcas pa gnas so //
NK068(nyu)001:10798: 'dir chos nyid dang ye shes kyi rtsa'i 'od dkar
NK068(nyu)001:10799: po dang ser por byas pa ni dpe chung rang
NK068(nyu)001:10802: chos nyid ser po dang ye shes mthing gar bshad do //
NK068(nyu)001:10803: de ltar snying gi dkyil 'khor rtsa chen bzhi dang
NK068(nyu)001:10804: ldan pa de'i nang na dwangs ma lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK068(nyu)001:10805: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i dbus su ye shes gnyen
NK068(nyu)001:10806: po'i thig le me tog kun+da lta bu 'od sna
NK068(nyu)001:10807: tshogs cir yang ma nges pa mtha' thams cad las
NK068(nyu)001:10808: grol ba stong gsal 'gags pa med pa bde ba
NK068(nyu)001:10809: chen po'i ngo bor bzhugs te /
NK068(nyu)001:10810: de nyid ni ye nas bzhugs pa ltar lam pas
NK068(nyu)001:10811: thig le'i dkyil 'khor yungs 'bru tsam 'od lnga'i gong
NK068(nyu)001:10812: bu can gsal ba yul gyis mi 'phrog pa bsgom
NK068(nyu)001:10813: par byas pas / dwangs ma lnga ye shes snying
NK068(nyu)001:10814: po dang drug ye shes drug gi dkyil 'khor du
NK068(nyu)001:10815: rang snang ba ni phyin ci ma log pa'i yongs
NK068(nyu)001:10816: par byas pas / grub bo // de la spyi
NK068(nyu)001:10817: bor tshangs pa'i bu ga nas mar sems gtad de
NK068(nyu)001:10818: bsgoms pas ye shes lnga'i snying po'i dkyil 'khor te
NK068(nyu)001:10819: thig le 'od 'bar ba las byung ba'i 'od kyis
NK068(nyu)001:10820: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge bskul ba 'od du
NK068(nyu)001:10821: 'bar bas sbyang bya'i yi ge drug gnyid dang bcas
NK068(nyu)001:10822: par byas pas / grub bo // pa sbyangs nas
NK068(nyu)001:10823: / las dang bag chags thams cad chos nyid du
NK068(nyu)001:10824: grol zhing dwangs ma lnga ye shes snying po la
NK068(nyu)001:10825: bsdus pas bde ba'i ye shes 'byung ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10826: rlung sems kyi dwangs ma thams cad thugs kyi dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:10827: 'khor der rdzogs pa'i tshe snang cha 'od lnga dang
NK068(nyu)001:10828: stong cha dbyings gnyis ro gcig tu 'dres pas tshogs
NK068(nyu)001:10829: gnyis rdzogs te sku gnyis mngon du gyur nas 'tshang
NK068(nyu)001:10830: rgya ba'i phyir 'di ni dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10831: nang nas mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10832: rnal 'byor pa 'chi ba'i tshe rlung dang dwangs ma
NK068(nyu)001:10833: thams cad dbu mar 'dus pa las rim bzhin 'chi
NK068(nyu)001:10834: srid stong pa'i 'od gsal dang rigs lnga'i tshom bu'i
NK068(nyu)001:10835: snang ba 'char ba'ang 'di'i gnad kyis 'byung bar bzhed
NK068(nyu)001:10837: gsang ba'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10838: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab drug cu
NK068(nyu)001:10839: rtsa bzhi'i dbus na dbyings phyug lnga'i thig le zhes
NK068(nyu)001:10840: bya ba yi ge a thung gi dbyibs su gnas
NK068(nyu)001:10841: te yum gyi gsang ba'i mkha'i sna rtse'i thig le
NK068(nyu)001:10843: de ni chos dbyings zab mo gsang ba kun tu
NK068(nyu)001:10844: bzang mo'i rang bzhin nyi ma'i thig le ste dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:10845: 'khor thams cad kyi phyi mor gyur pas dbyings so
NK068(nyu)001:10846: // de'i rang bzhin ni shes rab dang thabs te /
NK068(nyu)001:10847: gang zhe na thig le de las 'byung ba lnga'i
NK068(nyu)001:10848: dwangs ma cha phra ba'i rang bzhin med pa'i dbyings
NK068(nyu)001:10849: ni shes rab ste rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10850: chen po rags pa'i cha ni thabs rigs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa ste yab lnga'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10851: de ltar thig le byang chub kyi sems thabs shes dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10852: de las byung ba'i rtog tshogs dbang po dang yul
NK068(nyu)001:10853: dang dus dang yul so sor rigs par byed pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10854: rnam shes rnams sems dpa' dang 'joms byed yab yum
NK068(nyu)001:10855: sogs thams cad ye shes chen po'i ngo bor rnam
NK068(nyu)001:10856: par dag pa kun tu bzang mo'i dkyil 'khor yin
NK068(nyu)001:10857: la / de thams cad kyang rang byung gi ye shes su rdzogs pas bdag nyid chen po ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10858: de dang kha sbyor snying ga'i 'khor lo la rgyal
NK068(nyu)001:10859: ba kun gyi lhag pa'i dgongs pa zab mo thugs
NK068(nyu)001:10860: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi snang cha ye
NK068(nyu)001:10861: shes lnga ye nas lhun grub tu gnas pa ste
NK068(nyu)001:10862: / de'i lta ba ni snying ga nas mar lte
NK068(nyu)001:10863: ba'i thig le la sems gtad de bsgoms pas snying
NK068(nyu)001:10864: ga'i thig le'i 'od dang dwangs ma'i drod rtsa a
NK068(nyu)001:10865: ba d+hu ti nas mar nar gyis song bas dbyings
NK068(nyu)001:10866: phyung lnga'i thig ler phog ste 'od du 'bar bas
NK068(nyu)001:10867: rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su gsal ba gyur
NK068(nyu)001:10868: / / de'i drod slar yang song ste snying ga'i
NK068(nyu)001:10869: dwangs ma la thim pas dwangs ma'i bde drod ches
NK068(nyu)001:10870: cher 'bar bas na rags pa'i las rlung gi rgyu
NK068(nyu)001:10871: ba 'gags pas thig le 'gro 'ong med par snying
NK068(nyu)001:10872: ga'i gnas las mi g.yo bar gnas pas bde ba
NK068(nyu)001:10873: chen po rang rigs pa'i ye shes rang shar ba
NK068(nyu)001:10874: la blta bya lta byed med pa'i tshul gyis blta
NK068(nyu)001:10875: zhing nyams su len pa ni mthong ba med pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10876: tshul gyis mthong ba dam pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10877: de ni lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo bsgom pa'i man ngag go //
NK068(nyu)001:10879: snying po'i thig le sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10880: de yang mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo rtsa
NK068(nyu)001:10881: 'dab bcu drug gi dbus na mkha' 'gro ma rngams
NK068(nyu)001:10882: ma zhes bya ba yi ge am gi rnam par
NK068(nyu)001:10883: gnas pa la bza' btung gi bcud 'dus pas na
NK068(nyu)001:10885: snying ga'i dwangs ma chen po'i 'od dang drod yar
NK068(nyu)001:10886: song ste mgrin pa longs spyod kyi thig le la
NK068(nyu)001:10887: phog pas rtog tshogs kyi thig le'i 'khyag pa bzhu
NK068(nyu)001:10888: ste zhu ba'i dwangs ma snying gar mched /
NK068(nyu)001:10889: dbugs thig ler thim pas rlung dang rtog pa 'gags
NK068(nyu)001:10890: te 'khor lo gnyis bde ba dus gcig tu mnyam
NK068(nyu)001:10891: par sbyor zhing / de ltar sbyar bas bde ba
NK068(nyu)001:10892: chen po la gnas pa'i rang gdangs ye shes lngar
NK068(nyu)001:10893: ma 'gags pa'i rol mo yis drod rtsa rlung gsum
NK068(nyu)001:10894: gcig tu 'dres te bde gsal rnam par mi rtog
NK068(nyu)001:10895: pa'i ye shes mi g.yo bar rang gsal ba'i dgyes
NK068(nyu)001:10896: pa chen po la yul yul can gnyis med kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10897: ngang du mchod pa 'bul zhes bya ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10898: mgrin pa'i 'khor lo bsgom pa'i man ngag go //
NK068(nyu)001:10900: zag pa sogs rkang pa dgu ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10901: spyi bor bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab sum
NK068(nyu)001:10902: cu rtsa gnyis kyi dbus na kun tu bzang po
NK068(nyu)001:10903: zla ba'i thig le yi ge ham gi dbyibs su
NK068(nyu)001:10904: gnas te de bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis zag pa med
NK068(nyu)001:10905: pa'i bde ba nyams su myong ba'i bsod nams kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10906: tshogs rdzogs te dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10907: dri ma dag nas ye shes sgyu mar rang snang
NK068(nyu)001:10908: ba'o // de yang snying ga nas me sna yar song ste longs spyod kyi thig le la phog /
NK068(nyu)001:10909: de nas yar spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas
NK068(nyu)001:10910: thon te phyoogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK068(nyu)001:10911: thams cad la phog pas 'od du zhu nas tshur
NK068(nyu)001:10912: 'dus bde chen gyi 'khor lo na thig le ham
NK068(nyu)001:10914: ham yang 'od du zhu ba las rtsa 'dab so
NK068(nyu)001:10915: gnyis kyi rtog tshogs kyi thig le 'od du zhu
NK068(nyu)001:10916: ste / zag med kyi bde bas lus mgo mjug
NK068(nyu)001:10917: ma lus par khyab tsa na rtog tshogs thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:10918: sku dang ye shes su gsal ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10919: de yang rtogs dka' bas gsang ba bcud 'dus pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10920: thig le bde ba'i ye shes de nyid kyi 'byung
NK068(nyu)001:10921: khungs su gyur bas dbyings zhes bya ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10922: bde ba'i ye shes de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos gazhi'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10923: de ltar rnal 'byor pa bde ba chen po'i chos
NK068(nyu)001:10924: kyi skur gyur pa na phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis
NK068(nyu)001:10925: bsdus pa'i chos thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum
NK068(nyu)001:10926: du gsal bar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi sku
NK068(nyu)001:10927: dang gsung dang yon tan phrin las dang thugs rnam
NK068(nyu)001:10928: pa lnga'am nyer lnga ma lus pa bdag nyid kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10929: zhal bdag nyid kyis mthong ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10930: des ni rig pa la rang dbang sgyur ba'i phyir
NK068(nyu)001:10931: na lam gyi nang nas mchog nyid dang thabs kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10932: nang nas dam pa yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:10933: spyi bo'i 'khor lo bsgom pa'i man ngag go //
NK068(nyu)001:10934: mdor na 'khor lo bzhi'i dwangs ma'i dwangs ma rnams
NK068(nyu)001:10935: 'khor lo bzhi'i lte ba'i dwangs ma g.yo byed dang
NK068(nyu)001:10936: bral ba'i 'od gsal la tshur thim pas bde gsal
NK068(nyu)001:10937: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes chen po gcig
NK068(nyu)001:10938: dang du ma med pa'i chos nyid mchog tu mi
NK068(nyu)001:10940: gnyis pa 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag ltar bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10941: thabs nyid shes rab tu dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10942: shes rab nyid thabs su dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10943: thabs shes dbyer med du sbyor ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10945: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10946: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor bde ba'i ye shes kyi ro
NK068(nyu)001:10947: dang ldan pa'i don de nyid gsang ba'i lung man
NK068(nyu)001:10948: ngag rig pa gsum gyis gtan la phab ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10949: rtogs par byed pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bzhi
NK068(nyu)001:10950: bsgom pa'i dkyil 'khor la ni bde ba'i ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:10951: bskyed par byed pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10952: de yang yum gyi mkha' dang skye mched rnams lha
NK068(nyu)001:10953: sngags su byin gyis brlabs te sbyor ba'i brda' bsnol
NK068(nyu)001:10954: mar bskul zhing yab thabs kyi dkyil 'khor dang yum
NK068(nyu)001:10955: shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis su med par rol
NK068(nyu)001:10956: pa las bde ba'i ye shes byung ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10957: yab kyi zla ba byang chub kyi sems la don
NK068(nyu)001:10958: dam gyi ye shes skye ba ni mi dmigs mtha'
NK068(nyu)001:10959: dang bral bas thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK068(nyu)001:10960: yab kyi thig le rdo rje bum pa'i nang na
NK068(nyu)001:10961: gnas pa'i dus na khams lnga'i bcud 'dus shing ye
NK068(nyu)001:10962: shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas na dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:10964: de ni thabs nyid shes rab tu sbyor ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:10966: gsang ba'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:10967: de'i tshe yum gyi nyi ma byang chub kyi sems
NK068(nyu)001:10968: kyi thig le la rtsa gnas thams cad kyi bcud
NK068(nyu)001:10969: 'dus pa de rtog dka' bas gsang ba'i thig le
NK068(nyu)001:10970: de nyid thabs kyis ma zin pa las 'khor ba
NK068(nyu)001:10972: thabs kyis zin na rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir dbyings so //
NK068(nyu)001:10974: 'byung lnga cha phra ba shes rab ste rigs kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10975: yum lnga dang chen po ni phung po lnga ste
NK068(nyu)001:10976: rigs kyi yab lnga nyid du lhun gyis grub cing
NK068(nyu)001:10977: / byang chub sems kyi bde bas rtog tshogs thams
NK068(nyu)001:10978: cad ni sku dang ye shes kyi rdo rje dbyer
NK068(nyu)001:10980: de'ang dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams lhar yongs
NK068(nyu)001:10981: su dag pas spyod yul kun tu bzang po'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:10982: 'khor la sems lnga mthar phyin pa'i lhan skyes bde
NK068(nyu)001:10983: ba'i ye shes zag pa med pa'i bdag nyid chen
NK068(nyu)001:10984: po skyes pa de nyams su myongs bas lhag pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10985: thugs kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo bde ba chen po'i
NK068(nyu)001:10986: ro ye shes lngar 'char ba la blta bya lta
NK068(nyu)001:10987: byed med pa'i tshul gyis blta zhing yum gyi nyi
NK068(nyu)001:10988: ma byang sems pad+ma'i ze'u 'brur gnas pa'i tshe nyi
NK068(nyu)001:10989: ma byang sems de nyid sku dang ye shes kyi
NK068(nyu)001:10990: dkyil 'khor du rang gsal ba ni shes rab nyid
NK068(nyu)001:10993: snying po'i thig le sogs tshig bcad gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:10994: yab yum gyi rtsa thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:10995: nyi zla gnyis su med pa'i thig le la snying
NK068(nyu)001:10996: po'i thig le'o // yab kyi zla ba byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK068(nyu)001:10997: yum gyi nyi ma byang chub kyi sems gnyis ro mnyam zhing gnyis med du sbyor bas /
NK068(nyu)001:10998: mtha' gnyis las grol ba'i dngos po lhan cig skyes
NK068(nyu)001:10999: pa'i bde ba'i ye shes de lam pas nyams su
NK068(nyu)001:11000: myong zhing tshim pas na rol mo'i ye shes zhes
NK068(nyu)001:11001: bya'o // dga' ba bcu drug gi rim pas mas
NK068(nyu)001:11002: ldog gi bde ba'i ye shes nyams su myong bas
NK068(nyu)001:11003: rab tu dgyees par gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor la bde
NK068(nyu)001:11004: stong gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa 'bul zhes bya'o
NK068(nyu)001:11005: bya'o // // de la nyon mongs pa dang rnam
NK068(nyu)001:11006: rtog gi zag pa med pa'i ye shes kyi ro
NK068(nyu)001:11007: ma 'gags par myong ba bsod nams kyi tshogs kyis
NK068(nyu)001:11008: bde ba'i ye shes snang la 'dzin med sgyu ma
NK068(nyu)001:11009: lta bu nyams su myong bas 'dod chags nyid bde
NK068(nyu)001:11010: ba'i ye shes su rang snang la /
NK068(nyu)001:11011: de nyid sku dang ye shes su gsal bas yid
NK068(nyu)001:11012: ches tshim par byed pas na rol mo'i dkyil 'khor
NK068(nyu)001:11013: te / de nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pas na mtha' yas pa'i mchog go //
NK068(nyu)001:11014: nyi zla gnyis med kyi ye shes rtogs dka' ba
NK068(nyu)001:11015: gsang ba'i thig le de nyid sku dang ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:11016: kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas na dbyings so //
NK068(nyu)001:11017: de la thabs shes gnyis med du sbyor ba ste
NK068(nyu)001:11018: bde ba'i ye shes de ni dus gsum gyi rgyal
NK068(nyu)001:11019: ba kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos gzhi yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11020: de thob pa'i tshe phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rdzogs pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11021: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK068(nyu)001:11022: phrin las te 'bras bu'i chos nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK068(nyu)001:11023: ma lus pa mthar phyin par mngon du byas shing
NK068(nyu)001:11024: 'grub par 'gyur ba yin te mthong ba med pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11025: tshul gyis bdag nyid kyi zhal dus gcig tu mthong
NK068(nyu)001:11026: ba zhes bya'o // de ni 'dod chags bde ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:11027: ye shes su dbang sgyur bar byed pa'i lam gyi
NK068(nyu)001:11028: nang nas mchog nyid yin la thabs kyi nang nas
NK068(nyu)001:11030: de ltar thig le nyams su myong tshe gnas skabs la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11031: snyoms par zhugs pas dang po thig le gnas nas g.yos pa ni dga' ba /
NK068(nyu)001:11032: bde ba nyams su myong ba ni mchog dga' /
NK068(nyu)001:11033: bde ba'i ngo bor sems 'gags pas stong par grol ba ni dga' bral /
NK068(nyu)001:11034: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po bde stong dbyer med
NK068(nyu)001:11035: nyams su myong ba ni lhan skyes kyi dga' ba
NK068(nyu)001:11036: ste / lugs 'byung lugs ldog gi 'gros kyis dga'
NK068(nyu)001:11037: ba bzhi bzhi lus kyi gnas bzhi la yang sbyar
NK068(nyu)001:11038: ste / nas gsungs so // de re re la'ang
NK068(nyu)001:11039: dga' ba'i dga' ba sogs dga' chung bcu drug yod
NK068(nyu)001:11040: ste / nas gsungs so // de / de ltar
NK068(nyu)001:11041: yas babs kyi dga' bzhis rgyu'i sa lam dang mas
NK068(nyu)001:11042: brtan la 'bras bu'i sa lam dang khyad par gyi
NK068(nyu)001:11043: sa gsum dang bcas pa sbyar shes par bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11044: de ltar gzhung 'di nyid thugs thig dang gsang thig
NK068(nyu)001:11045: gi dgongs pa ltar rten gyi gang zag 'dod chags
NK068(nyu)001:11046: can gyi lam gyi cha rkyen tshang bar bstan pa
NK068(nyu)001:11047: yin no // gsum pa mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11048: dkyil 'khor la gnas sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:11049: de ltar lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK068(nyu)001:11050: dang byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la blo brtan
NK068(nyu)001:11051: par gnas pa'i stobs kyis bdag don du rang bzhin
NK068(nyu)001:11052: nyid kyi dkyil 'khor gzhi'i gnas lugs de nyid mngon
NK068(nyu)001:11053: du rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu mthar phyin rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:11054: 'khor de nyid rang rig la mngon sum du snang
NK068(nyu)001:11055: bas na lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11056: des na rang rig pa'i gnas lugs kyi rgyan du
NK068(nyu)001:11057: dkyil 'khor bdun gyis bsdus pa'i chos ma lus pa
NK068(nyu)001:11058: thams cad ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par rang snang
NK068(nyu)001:11060: 'o na rgyal ba'i snang ngo la chos thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:11061: gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas gdul
NK068(nyu)001:11062: bya sems can gyi snang ba med pa'i phyir thugs
NK068(nyu)001:11064: de yang gzhi rang bzhin dang 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11065: dkyil 'khor gnyis rang rig pa'i bdag nyid du mnyam
NK068(nyu)001:11066: par sbyor bas / gdul bya 'gro ba drug gi
NK068(nyu)001:11067: sems can thams cad kyang rgyal ba rang las mi
NK068(nyu)001:11068: gzhan pas na thugs rje'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang
NK068(nyu)001:11069: bas ma btsal lhun grub tu yongs kyis 'byung ste
NK068(nyu)001:11070: par sbyor bas / / gang zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11071: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa thams cad rgyal ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:11072: dkyil 'khor du rang snang nas gdul bya gang yang
NK068(nyu)001:11073: mi 'dor bar 'dul ba'i phyir sdug bsngal las skyobs
NK068(nyu)001:11076: dpe sgyu ma mkhan gyis sprul pa'i rta glang snang
NK068(nyu)001:11077: yang bden dngos kyis stong pa bzhin ye shes sgyu
NK068(nyu)001:11078: ma'i dkyil 'khor gzugs sku gnyis su snang nas 'gro
NK068(nyu)001:11079: ba sgrol bar byed pa yis don bya ba'i yul
NK068(nyu)001:11080: byed pa'i mkhan po don byas pa'i dngos po dang
NK068(nyu)001:11081: gsum du 'dzin pa med par rang rigs pa'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:11083: gnyis pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11084: ye shes rdzogs pa'i sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11085: de yang gzhi rang byung gi ye shes la 'bras
NK068(nyu)001:11086: bu'i chos thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK068(nyu)001:11087: gzhi ma bcos pa de nyid sems can thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:11088: kyi rgyud la ye nas gnas kyang /
NK068(nyu)001:11089: rang gi rtog pas bsgribs nas ma rtogs pa de
NK068(nyu)001:11090: rtogs par byed pa'i thabs thos pa'i shes rab kyis
NK068(nyu)001:11091: the tshom shes par byed cing /
NK068(nyu)001:11092: bsam pa'i shes rab kyi the tshom sel bar byed la /
NK068(nyu)001:11093: sgom pa'i shes rab kyis the tshom chod par byas pas te /
NK068(nyu)001:11094: de yang thos pas ming dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11095: bsam pa'i ming don gnyis ka dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11096: sgom pas don 'ba' zhig la mnyam par sbyor ba'i thabs kyis /
NK068(nyu)001:11097: rang byung ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rang rig pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11098: mngon sum du gsal ba ni 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK068(nyu)001:11100: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11101: de ltar gsang ba'i snying po'i lam gyi tshul 'di
NK068(nyu)001:11102: ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi 'bras
NK068(nyu)001:11103: bu'i ngo bo nyid thob par byed pa las 'da'
NK068(nyu)001:11104: bar mi mdzad pas na dam tshig gi mchog ces
NK068(nyu)001:11105: bya'o // gnyis pa de gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:11106: sgrub pa po gang zag gi che ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11107: sgrub thabs lam gyi che ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11109: gang zhig sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11110: sdig pa'i grogs dang bral bas blo phyin ci ma
NK068(nyu)001:11111: log pa'i gang zag gang zhig rgyud sde zab mo
NK068(nyu)001:11112: 'di 'ba' zhig lam nyams su len tshul 'di la
NK068(nyu)001:11113: mos par gyur ba tsam yang sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:11114: 'khor phyogs bcur bzhugs pa thams cad kyis phyogs dang
NK068(nyu)001:11116: rnam pa thams cad du gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ma
NK068(nyu)001:11117: lus rgyud la bsnyen te thob par byed pa'i nye
NK068(nyu)001:11118: ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur te /
NK068(nyu)001:11119: dper na sangs rgyas kyi sras nyan rang sogs yin
NK068(nyu)001:11120: la chos mthun bzhis byang chub sems dpa' rnams yin
NK068(nyu)001:11121: pa bzhin no // gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11122: lam kun gyi 'bras bu yin pa'i dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11123: rgyal ba'i gshegs shul yin pa'i dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11124: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam yin pa'i dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11125: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i zhe phug yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11127: bskal pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11128: dus bskal pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi rdul phran
NK068(nyu)001:11129: gyi grangs dang mnyam pa de nyid du rgyu'i theg
NK068(nyu)001:11130: par shin tu blo sbyangs pa la rab tu gnas
NK068(nyu)001:11132: gsang sngags phyi nang gi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK068(nyu)001:11133: bsnyen cing sgrub pa de thams cad kyis don du
NK068(nyu)001:11134: gnyer bya'i 'bras bu 'tshang rgya ba la lam gsang
NK068(nyu)001:11135: chen bla na med pa'i theg pa 'di kho na
NK068(nyu)001:11136: la rag las pa yin te gzhan med do //
NK068(nyu)001:11138: 'jig rten sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11139: de yang 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i gnas na
NK068(nyu)001:11140: 'das pa dang da ltar byung ba'i rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:11141: 'khor ma lus pas rgyu'i theg pa'i sgo nas dka'
NK068(nyu)001:11142: ba mang du spyad kyang 'bras bu mthar ma phyin
NK068(nyu)001:11143: pas de dag gsang ba'i snying po'i lam 'di bsnyen
NK068(nyu)001:11144: pa'am brten nas gzod sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11145: bdag nyid rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK068(nyu)001:11147: de'i phyir na rgyal ba'i gshegs shul yin pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11149: 'byung dang sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:11150: da ltar byung ba'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang ma
NK068(nyu)001:11151: 'ongs pa na 'byung bar 'gyur ba'i rnal 'byor pa
NK068(nyu)001:11152: thams cad kun kyang rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i
NK068(nyu)001:11153: don rtogs pa 'di yis sku lnga lhun gyis grub
NK068(nyu)001:11154: pa'i sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur bas na ma 'ongs
NK068(nyu)001:11155: pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam yin pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11157: 'di ni sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11158: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di ni ye nas gnas pa'i cha nas gzhi /
NK068(nyu)001:11159: de nyid nyams su len pa'i cha nas lam /
NK068(nyu)001:11160: de mngon du gyur ba'i cha nas 'bras bu ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11161: de ltar mtshan so sor btags kyang ngo bo nyid gcig pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11162: tha mi dad pa ni theg pa thun mong ba
NK068(nyu)001:11163: rnams kyi blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas na
NK068(nyu)001:11165: des na nges pa'i don mthar thug pa 'di ni 'bras bu yang yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:11166: de nyid nyams su len pa'i cha nas lam du yang gyur pa yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11167: de'i phyir rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:11168: 'khor lhag ma ma lus pa rnams kyi dgongs pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11170: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don thugs kyi brnag byar gyur pa gzhan med de /
NK068(nyu)001:11171: des na gzhan nas btsal kyang rtogs pa mngon du
NK068(nyu)001:11172: gyur pa'i rgyal bas kyang thob par byar med pas
NK068(nyu)001:11174: de'i phyir na dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11175: de la 'phros nas kha cig na re /
NK068(nyu)001:11176: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyi 'bras bu la lam du byed dam mi byed /
NK068(nyu)001:11178: byed na smin pa lam du byed dam /
NK068(nyu)001:11179: ma smin pa lam du byed /
NK068(nyu)001:11180: snga ma ltar na thug med du 'gyur te /
NK068(nyu)001:11181: smin pa lam du byed pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:11183: khyab pa tshad mas grub ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11184: na ning gi 'bras bu da gzod kyi sa bon du gyur pa bzhin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11186: phyi ma ltar na 'bras bu lam du byed pa ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK068(nyu)001:11187: ma smin pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11189: bskyed bya skyed byed rgyu 'bras kyi dbang du byas na de ltar yin kyang /
NK068(nyu)001:11190: 'dir ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu 'bras kyi dbang du 'bras bu ni ye nas smin zin yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:11191: yin pa la yin pa ltar nyams su len pa ni lam du byed pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11192: de'i dgos ched ni yin pa la yin pa ltar mngon du gyur ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11193: de'i phyir na gzhi lam 'bras bu ngo bo tha
NK068(nyu)001:11194: mi dad par rtogs shing nyams su len pa ni
NK068(nyu)001:11195: 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa'i khyad chos yin no
NK068(nyu)001:11196: // gal te lan rnal mas mi lo na tshes
NK068(nyu)001:11197: brgyad kyi zla ba 'di zla ba yin nam ma
NK068(nyu)001:11198: // yin zhes pa'am / bu chung mi yin nam
NK068(nyu)001:11199: min zhes mgo basgre'o zhes rgya gab gong pa gsungs
NK068(nyu)001:11200: // yin zhes pa'am / so // gsum pa yul
NK068(nyu)001:11201: gang la gdams pa'i snod bshad pa la gnyis te
NK068(nyu)001:11202: // yin zhes pa'am / so // / snod dang ldan pa la sbyin pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11203: snod min la mi sbyin par bstan pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11205: kun gyi sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11206: rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos gzhi phyag rgya
NK068(nyu)001:11207: chen po mchog gi rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po
NK068(nyu)001:11208: 'di su'i spyod yul yin zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11209: thos pa'i shes rab rngam po zan za ba lta bu dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11210: bsam pa'i shes rab gzon mo sha za ba lta bu dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11211: sgom pa'i shes rab bu chung zhun mar za ba lta bu ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11212: de ltar shes rab gsum la blo sbyangs pa'i stobs
NK068(nyu)001:11213: kyis dngos po thams cad kyi de kho na nyid
NK068(nyu)001:11214: mthong ba ni shes rab kyi mig ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11215: de dang ldan pa'i skyes bu rnams kyis rgyud 'di zungs shig ces pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11216: de yang gzhi dad pa med pa snod kha sbubs pa'i skyon /
NK068(nyu)001:11217: grogs brtson 'grus med pa snod zhabs brdol gyi skyon /
NK068(nyu)001:11218: man ngag zabaga mo gsang mi thub pa snod gzhog ral gyi skyon /
NK068(nyu)001:11219: chags sdang dang phrag dog la sogs pa'i phyir du chos byed pa snod dug can gyi skyon /
NK068(nyu)001:11220: de ltar snod kyi skyon bzhi dang bral ba /
NK068(nyu)001:11221: shes rab dang snying rje sogs thub pas snod kyi yon tan lnga dang ldan pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11223: ngang chu bo chen po'i rgyun bzhin ring ba /
NK068(nyu)001:11224: tshul dge slong gsar bu ltar zhib pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11225: bsam pa rin po che gser ltar bzang ba /
NK068(nyu)001:11226: blo ri rab ltar brtan cing mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11227: yang na cis kyang sems mi 'khrugs pas ngang bzang ba /
NK068(nyu)001:11228: skye bo rnams kyi spyod pa las ldog pas tshul shes pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11229: blo mi 'gyur bas rab tu brtan cing /
NK068(nyu)001:11230: lus dang longs spyod thams cad chos phyir ser sna
NK068(nyu)001:11231: med par gtong phod pa la rgyud 'di sbyin par
NK068(nyu)001:11233: gzhan du sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11234: de las gzhan du snod min la nam yang sbyin par mi bya ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11235: nyes pa chen po bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:11237: rmongs pa la 'phyar bas gsang mi thub par gal
NK068(nyu)001:11238: te sbyin na ma dang mkha' 'gro'i bka'i chad pas
NK068(nyu)001:11239: 'chi ba'i dus min par glo bur du ni srog
NK068(nyu)001:11240: gi dbang po zad nas tshe'i dus byed cing /
NK068(nyu)001:11241: shi ma thag tsha dmyal gyi mes bsregs pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11242: grang dmyal gyis chus sbrebs par byed pa'i sdug bsngal
NK068(nyu)001:11243: la yun ring gnas te nyam thag par 'gyur ro
NK068(nyu)001:11244: // de yang 'grel pa spar khab las /
NK068(nyu)001:11245: bskal pa chen po gsum du dmyal bar gnas so //
NK068(nyu)001:11246: de las thar nas bskal pa gnyis su yi dwags su gnas so //
NK068(nyu)001:11247: de nas kyang sangs rgyas kyi sgra thos par daka'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11250: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK068(nyu)001:11253: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la sbyin //
NK068(nyu)001:11254: zhes pa gnyis ldabs so zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11256: gong ma ni theg pa 'og ma rnams la sbyangs
NK068(nyu)001:11257: pa'i 'bras bu 'di nyid 'grub tshul gyi sgo nas
NK068(nyu)001:11259: skabs 'dir ni snod kyi skyon dang yon tan bstan pa yin pas so //
NK068(nyu)001:11261: le'u lnga par yo byad ldan zhes grol lam rim gyis pa'i tshogs sgrub gcig bstan /
NK068(nyu)001:11262: dgu par yang cho ga lnga ni zhes sogs kyis tshogs sgrub gcig bstan /
NK068(nyu)001:11263: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis par yang yan lag ma nyams sogs kyis tshogs sgrub bstan /
NK068(nyu)001:11264: bcu gsum pa 'dir yang byung bas de dag zlos so zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11265: dgos ched so so'i dbang gis mi zlos te /
NK068(nyu)001:11266: lnga par ni rgyu tshang bas phyag rgya gcig spros
NK068(nyu)001:11267: las su rung nas yi ge sgyu 'phrul bsgrubs pas
NK068(nyu)001:11268: dngos grub gnyis kyi thob tshul yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:11269: dgu par zab moo'i dbang thob nas tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11270: gnas skabs su tshe dbang dang mthar thug tu sku
NK068(nyu)001:11271: lnga la sbyor ba'i dus gtso bor bstan pa yin
NK068(nyu)001:11272: cing / bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis par gzhi
NK068(nyu)001:11273: phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang thabs bsnyen bsgrub bzhi
NK068(nyu)001:11274: rgyas par bstan pas sgrub pa'i yan lag tshang zhing
NK068(nyu)001:11275: cing / / gtso bor mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor
NK068(nyu)001:11276: sgrol la spyod pas gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi
NK068(nyu)001:11277: 'bras bu la sbyor tshul yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:11278: bcu gsum pa 'dir ni dgag bya gzhan gyis brtags
NK068(nyu)001:11279: pa'i ma rtogs log rtogs bsal nas thun mong gi
NK068(nyu)001:11280: lam nas 'grod pa'i mtha' 'di'i lam mngon du byed
NK068(nyu)001:11281: tshul gtso bor bstan pa yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11284: de skad ces ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK068(nyu)001:11285: kyis 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched
NK068(nyu)001:11289: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis su yod pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:11290: 'dis theg pa 'og ma rnams la shin tu gsang
NK068(nyu)001:11291: ba'i don tshe 'di nyid la grol ba'i thabs mchog
NK068(nyu)001:11292: tu gyur pa nye bar bstan pa'i man ngag zab
NK068(nyu)001:11293: cing snying por dril ba'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o
NK068(nyu)001:11295: // // da ni le'u bcu bzhi pa 'chad par byed pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:11296: chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na /
NK068(nyu)001:11297: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam dang 'bras bu ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11298: lam la thabs grol gnyis las grol lam ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11299: rim cig car gnyis las gnyis ka ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11300: mtshan nyid gsum las 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11301: snang ba bzhi las lam dang 'bras bu'i snang ba ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11302: 'bring gi chos lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11303: de la bcu las bstod pa'i mchod pa ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11304: zhor la dkyil 'khor dang phrin las ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11306: spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston par byed do //
NK068(nyu)001:11307: de ltar ston pa'i le'u 'di la gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11313: lam thabs grol gyi man ngag snying por bstan pa
NK068(nyu)001:11314: de nas rang snang gi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11315: phyir du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag
NK068(nyu)001:11316: po rigs drug pas nyid kyi che ba'i yon tan
NK068(nyu)001:11317: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang
NK068(nyu)001:11318: ba la dgyes pa chen po'i glu drug po 'di
NK068(nyu)001:11319: blangs so // gnyis pa gzhung la gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11320: 'bras chos nyer lnga so sor bstod pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11324: dang po sku lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11326: ni ye shes lnga'i yi ge glu'i 'go 'dren par byed pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11328: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba thams cad rang rig
NK068(nyu)001:11329: pa'i ye shes gcig la lhun gyis grub par rdzogs
NK068(nyu)001:11330: pas sku gsum snang ba'i go 'byed pa ni mngon
NK068(nyu)001:11332: rig pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dbyings thig le
NK068(nyu)001:11333: chen po'i klong du grol ba ni chos kyi sku'o
NK068(nyu)001:11334: // gang yang ma spangs pa'i zag pa med pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11335: bsod nams kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba ni
NK068(nyu)001:11337: gdul bya thams cad kyi ngo la dus thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:11338: du sku yi snang ba sna tshogs su cir yang
NK068(nyu)001:11339: snang ba'i phyir sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11340: snang stong gnyis med du zlum pas na thig le
NK068(nyu)001:11341: ste 'khor 'das kyi chos kun dbyer med du rdzogs
NK068(nyu)001:11343: bstod bas mnyes par gyur pas hohzhesa bya ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11344: kun la mthun par shes par bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11345: gnyis pa gsung lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11347: ni ye shes lnga ldan gsung lnga mtshon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11348: gsung lnga skye 'jig med par dbyer mi phyed pas rdo rje zhes bya ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11349: bsod nams kyi ngo bo sgra thams cad ma spangs
NK068(nyu)001:11350: par rang snang ba'i phyir brjod pa tshig gi gsung
NK068(nyu)001:11351: ngo // spros pa med pas na thig le chen
NK068(nyu)001:11352: po'i rang bzhin brjod du med pa'i phyir skye med
NK068(nyu)001:11354: rdo rje ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor rang rig pa
NK068(nyu)001:11355: la ldan pas na de nyid tshig tu brjod par
NK068(nyu)001:11356: rig par gsal bas brda' sprod pas mnyam nyid rig
NK068(nyu)001:11357: pa'i gsung ngo // rdo rje'i sgra chen po tshig
NK068(nyu)001:11358: gcig gis don mtha' yas pa go bar byed pa'am
NK068(nyu)001:11359: pa'i gsung ngo // / rdo rje'i gsung sgra chen
NK068(nyu)001:11360: po gcig la gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu sogs
NK068(nyu)001:11361: mtha' yas par grags pa'i phyiir tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi
NK068(nyu)001:11362: pa'i gsung ngo // / gsung ngo // yi ge'am
NK068(nyu)001:11363: tshig tu brjod pa med pa nyid brjod pa dang
NK068(nyu)001:11364: 'dra bar 'khor gyi blo la gsal ba ni gsung
NK068(nyu)001:11365: gi rab bam rgyal po yin pa'i phyir dgongs pa
NK068(nyu)001:11366: pa'i gsung ngo // / gsung ngo // brda'i gsung
NK068(nyu)001:11367: ngo // rgyal ba'i gsung lnga dbyer med du zlum
NK068(nyu)001:11368: pa'i thig le chen po grags stong dbyer mi phyed
NK068(nyu)001:11369: pa ni yi ge med pa rdo rje'i gsung ngo
NK068(nyu)001:11370: pa'i gsung ngo // / gsung ngo // brda'i gsung ngo // // hohni mnyes pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11371: gsum pa thugs lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11373: ni ye shes lnga ldan thugs lnga mtshon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11374: me long ye shes ni ye shes gzhan gsum po 'char gzhi'i rten byed pas sku dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11375: sor rtog ye shes ni shes bya thams cad ma 'dres par gzigs nas chos ston pas gsung dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11376: chos dbyings ye shes ni snying por gyur pas thugs kyi thugs te /
NK068(nyu)001:11377: de gsum rdzoogs pa'i bdag nyid chen po de la
NK068(nyu)001:11378: yon tan ma lus pa 'byung bas mnyam nyid dang
NK068(nyu)001:11379: / gdul bya 'dul ba'i phrin las bya grub ye shes kyang kun tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11380: de ltar ye nas ye shes lngar lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin te /
NK068(nyu)001:11381: ye shes re re la'ang lnga lnga 'dus pa'i tshogs
NK068(nyu)001:11382: rang byung gi ye shes chen po gcig gi ngo
NK068(nyu)001:11383: bor 'dus ba'i thig le che hohzhesa mnyes pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11384: bzhi pa yon tan lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11386: ni ye shes lnga ldan yon tan lnga mtshon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11387: sems nyid gang du'ang mi dmigs pa'i rig pa sgyu
NK068(nyu)001:11388: ma nyid gzhal yas khang sna tshogs su 'phrul zhing
NK068(nyu)001:11389: snang bas snang stong gnyis su med par mnyam pa
NK068(nyu)001:11391: phyi nang dang rgya che chung gzhal du med pa'i phyir gzhal yas khang gi yon tan no //
NK068(nyu)001:11392: rgyal ba drug pa'i zhing khams la yon tan mtha'
NK068(nyu)001:11393: yas pa dang ldan pa dus dang rnam pa kun
NK068(nyu)001:11394: tu snang nas don mdzad pa ni zhing khams kyi
NK068(nyu)001:11395: yon tan no // ba spu'i bu ga re re
NK068(nyu)001:11396: nas kyang ye shes lnga'i 'od zer kha dog sna
NK068(nyu)001:11397: tshogs pa 'phro ba ni 'od zer gyi yon tan
NK068(nyu)001:11398: yon tan no // no // gzugs sgra dri ro
NK068(nyu)001:11399: reg bya la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i
NK068(nyu)001:11400: lha mo grangs med pa re re yang mtha' yas
NK068(nyu)001:11401: pa'i 'dod pa'i yon tan kun nas lhun gyis grub
NK068(nyu)001:11402: yon tan no // no // cing / gzugs kyi
NK068(nyu)001:11403: lha mo la sogs pa spyan la sogs pa la
NK068(nyu)001:11404: thim pa ni longs spyod kyi yon tan no //
NK068(nyu)001:11405: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa'i yon tan
NK068(nyu)001:11406: sna tshogs lhun gyis grub pa seng ge la sogs
NK068(nyu)001:11407: pas sems can chen po lngas btegs pa'i khri'i steng
NK068(nyu)001:11408: du sku zla ba gsung nyi ma thugs nyes pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11409: skyon gyis ma gos pa'i pad+ma dang yon tan lhun
NK068(nyu)001:11410: gyis grub pas rin po che'i khri rkang chen por
NK068(nyu)001:11411: rang snang ba ni gdan khri'i yon tan no //
NK068(nyu)001:11413: lnga pa phrin las lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11415: ni ye shes lnga ldan phrin las lnga mtshon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11416: don bya ba'i yul phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK068(nyu)001:11417: rdul phra mo snyed kyi dag pa chos sku'i zhing
NK068(nyu)001:11418: khams ma dag sprul sku'i zhing khams bar ma longs
NK068(nyu)001:11419: sku'i zhing khams dang gsum du don bya ba'i rgyu
NK068(nyu)001:11420: rgyal ba'i mdzad pas sems can gyi don mdzad pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11421: phrin las rdul phran snyed rnams kyang zhi ba dang
NK068(nyu)001:11422: rgyas pa dang dbang dang drag po'i phrin las dang
NK068(nyu)001:11423: bzhir 'du la / don byed pa'i mkhan po zhi
NK068(nyu)001:11424: ba dang khro bo la sogs pa zhi rgyas dbang
NK068(nyu)001:11425: drag gi tshul du sprul pa'i grangs rgyal ba'i zhing
NK068(nyu)001:11426: gi rdul phran las 'das pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK068(nyu)001:11427: pa mtha' yas pa rnams kyis don byed do //
NK068(nyu)001:11428: don byed pa'i tshul gong gi sprul pa de dag
NK068(nyu)001:11429: gis dus skad cig gam yud tsam la rtsol ba
NK068(nyu)001:11430: la rag ma lus par phrin las bzhis don mdzad
NK068(nyu)001:11431: pa ni ma btsal bar gzhan don zin pa'i phyir
NK068(nyu)001:11432: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las zhes bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11434: gnyis pa spyir bstod pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11436: ye shes lnga ldan sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga mtshon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11437: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11438: chos lhag ma ma lus pa thams cad sku gsung
NK068(nyu)001:11439: thugs yon tan phrin las lngar ye nas gnas pa
NK068(nyu)001:11440: yin te / gnas tshul ji ltar zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11441: gangs ri chen po lnga'i dbus su mtsho gcig yod
NK068(nyu)001:11442: na de'i nang du gangs chen po'i gzugs brnyan lnga
NK068(nyu)001:11444: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi mdzad pa
NK068(nyu)001:11445: ji ltar snang yang gcig gi bdag nyid du 'dus
NK068(nyu)001:11446: pas na chen po zhes pa'am /
NK068(nyu)001:11447: yang na sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i
NK068(nyu)001:11448: ngo bo ni chos thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen
NK068(nyu)001:11449: po'o // yang mtsho chen po lnga'i dbus su gangs
NK068(nyu)001:11450: chen po gcig yod na mtsho re re'i nang du
NK068(nyu)001:11451: yang gangs chen po'i gzugs brnyan re re snang ba
NK068(nyu)001:11452: po'o // bzhin du / sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK068(nyu)001:11453: phrin las lnga char gyis 'khor 'das kyi chos re
NK068(nyu)001:11454: re la'ang kun tu khyab pa yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11455: des na dpe mtsho gcig tu gangs lnga 'char la
NK068(nyu)001:11456: gangs gcig mtsho lngar 'char ba bzhin sku gsung thugs
NK068(nyu)001:11457: yon tan phrin las kyi snang tshul kun gcig tu
NK068(nyu)001:11458: 'dus la / gcig kun tu 'char bas na phan
NK068(nyu)001:11459: tshun tha mi dad pa kho na'i phyir gcig dang
NK068(nyu)001:11460: du ma'i mtha' las grol ba yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:11461: de'i phyir thig le chen po'i rang bzhin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11463: gsum pa gsungs pa'i tshul ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11464: zhes ched du bsgrags so zhes pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11465: zhes glu drug gi don 'di dag ston pas 'khor rnams kyi ched du bsgrags so //
NK068(nyu)001:11466: de ltar bstod pa de dag kyang sgro btags pa'am skur pa btab pa ni ma yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:11467: yon tan yod pa la yod pa ltar du che ba'i yon tan la bstod pa yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11468: de'i phyir na yon tan med bzhin bstod pa ni sgro btags pa yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:11469: yod bzhin mi bstod pa ni skur pa btab pa yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11472: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis su yod pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:11473: 'dis mnyes pa chen po'i glus nyid kyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11475: // 'dir 'o na mnyes pa'i le'u bya ba 'dug pas
NK068(nyu)001:11476: rgyal ba la mnyes mi mnyes mnga' na gzung 'dzin
NK068(nyu)001:11478: rgyal ba la mnyes mi mnyes mi mnga' yang /
NK068(nyu)001:11479: gdul bya rnams tshogs gnyis rdzogs par bya ba'i ched
NK068(nyu)001:11480: du mnyes pa ltar snang ba la 'gal ba med
NK068(nyu)001:11481: do // de ltar le'u bcu bzhi pa yan chad
NK068(nyu)001:11482: ni rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba zhes kyang bya ste
NK068(nyu)001:11483: thugs rje zhi ba'i rgyud don gyi chos rnams rdzogs
NK068(nyu)001:11485: da ni le'u bco lnga pa 'chad par byed pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:11486: chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na /
NK068(nyu)001:11487: blo rab kyis chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las 'khrul gzhi gtso cher ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11488: r+au tra'i ngo la rgyal ba khro bor snang bas 'bras bu dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11489: r+au tras lam bgrod pas lam ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11490: lam la thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11493: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11494: rim cig char gnyis las gnyis ka ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11495: snang ba bzhi las 'khrul gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu'i snang ba ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11496: 'bring gi chos lnga las gleng bzhi dang rgyud don ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11497: rgyud don la bcu las gzhung hril pos khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11498: de'i sbyor la spyod pa ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11499: r+au tra la dbang bskur bas dbang ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11500: r+au tra la dam 'bogs pas dam tshig ston /
NK068(nyu)001:11507: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK068(nyu)001:11508: de ltar ston pa'i le'u 'di la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:11512: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mngon par 'du mdzad tshul mdor bstan /
NK068(nyu)001:11513: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11515: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:11516: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas khro bo'i
NK068(nyu)001:11517: dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa rigs
NK068(nyu)001:11518: thams cad kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang
NK068(nyu)001:11519: po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi
NK068(nyu)001:11520: ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa nyid kyis rang snang
NK068(nyu)001:11521: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor las ma g.yos par
NK068(nyu)001:11522: 'dul byed sprul pa'i sku khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ji
NK068(nyu)001:11523: ltar 'tshams pa mngon par 'du mdzad de /
NK068(nyu)001:11525: mnyam nyid ngang gis khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK068(nyu)001:11526: khro bas longs spyod rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK068(nyu)001:11527: rdo rje 'du 'phro mdzad la phyag mtshal lo //
NK068(nyu)001:11529: spyir khro bo la bzhi ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11533: phrin las phyag rgya'i khro bo'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11535: bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis dngos po dang
NK068(nyu)001:11536: mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i zhen pa thams cad 'joms pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11537: phyir te / sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK068(nyu)001:11538: yang dag shes rab chen po ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11539: mtshan ma 'joms phyir khro bo mchog /
NK068(nyu)001:11542: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis log rtog 'khor ba'i sa bon drung nas 'joms par byed pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11544: rang rig ye shes rgyal po yis //
NK068(nyu)001:11545: phyogs bcu'i khams rnams dbang bsdus nas //
NK068(nyu)001:11546: kun kyang mi dmigs dbyings su thim //
NK068(nyu)001:11547: thams cad khro bo'i tshogs su 'gyur //
NK068(nyu)001:11550: thugs rje'i shugs kyis 'gro ba skyob pa na 'bad
NK068(nyu)001:11551: rtsol med par mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad 'joms
NK068(nyu)001:11552: pa'i phyir te / rtog pa lta rgyud las /
NK068(nyu)001:11553: 'dzin pa med rtogs thugs rje zhen chags khro //
NK068(nyu)001:11556: gdug pa can rnams kyi mos ngor phrin las phyag rgya'i skur snang ba yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:11558: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK068(nyu)001:11559: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK068(nyu)001:11560: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK068(nyu)001:11561: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK068(nyu)001:11564: drang srong khros pa'i cha byad can dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11565: mi'u thung khros pa'i cha byad can dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11566: dpal chen rngams brjid kyi cha byad can dang gsum las /
NK068(nyu)001:11567: 'dir dpal chen rngams brjid kyi cha byad can te 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu dang ldan pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11568: 'o na dngos po'i gnas lugs la zhi khro gnyis gcig pa zhig gam tha dad pa yin /
NK068(nyu)001:11569: dang po ltar na gnyis su bshad pa dang 'gal la /
NK068(nyu)001:11570: gnyis pa ltar na kun khyab gsum gyis gnod byed yod de /
NK068(nyu)001:11573: rang bzhin chos skur gcig ma yin par 'gyur te /
