NK068(nyu)001:11576: tha dad la gcig ma yin pas khyab la /
NK068(nyu)001:11577: dper na lhas sbyin dang mchod sbyin bzhin no //
NK068(nyu)001:11578: 'dod na gong nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo
NK068(nyu)001:11579: bo nyid kyis zhes ngo bo gcig tu bshad pas
NK068(nyu)001:11580: gsal lo // gzhan yang zhi ba las khro bo bsgyur du mi btub par 'gyur te /
NK068(nyu)001:11584: khro ba'i rang bzhin shin tu gdug cing 'jigs pa ma yin zhing //
NK068(nyu)001:11585: zhi ba mdzad pas kun gyi yid la 'thad par gnas 'gyur yod ma yin /
NK068(nyu)001:11586: de gnyis gnyis su med pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK068(nyu)001:11590: sgyur ba'i 'khor lo de bzhin te //
NK068(nyu)001:11591: zhes pa la sogs pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:11592: 'dir kha cig zhi khro res mos pa 'gog pa ni 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:11593: gang zag gcig gis gnyis car bsgom par nges shing rtog gnyis cig car 'jug pa med la /
NK068(nyu)001:11594: bsgyur ba ni res mos pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:11596: lam pas bskyed cing bsgom bya zhi khro gnyis po chos can /
NK068(nyu)001:11597: dngos po'i gnas lugs la dbyer med pa yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:11598: gzhi sems nyid la tha dad du ma grub cing /
NK068(nyu)001:11599: lam ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgyur du btub la /
NK068(nyu)001:11600: 'bras bu la de gnyis rgyud so sor ma grub ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11601: rang bzhin chos skur gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:11604: gang gis ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs /
NK068(nyu)001:11607: rgyu gang gis gol ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11608: gol ba'i 'bras bu ji ltar smin pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11610: de ci'i phyir nas rmongs pas zhes pa'i bar te /
NK068(nyu)001:11611: de ltar 'dul byed khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mngon par
NK068(nyu)001:11612: 'du mdzad pa de dgos ched ci'i phyir zhe na
NK068(nyu)001:11614: gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i ched du'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11615: gdug pa can de su zhig snyam pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:11616: spyir 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bdag tu rmongs pa ma
NK068(nyu)001:11617: rig pa'i rnam par rtog pas nga dang bdag tu
NK068(nyu)001:11618: zhen pa dang / chos thams cad blos sgro btags tsam las bden par grub pa ma yin kyang /
NK068(nyu)001:11619: phyin ci log gis gzung yul la bdag gir mngon par zhen pas 'khor bar 'khyams shing gdungs la /
NK068(nyu)001:11620: de las nges par 'byin byed yang dag pa'i lam
NK068(nyu)001:11621: dang bral ba dag ni srid pa'i gnas su 'du
NK068(nyu)001:11623: de'i steng du khyad par r+au tra ni gab pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11624: gsang ba gnas lugs de bzhin nyid ma rtogs par
NK068(nyu)001:11625: sbas pa'i gsang ba sgrol ba dang sbyor ba sogs
NK068(nyu)001:11626: spyod pa barlanga po la mngon par 'chel nas 'byol
NK068(nyu)001:11628: de yang rgyud las dge sdig dang 'bras bu bde
NK068(nyu)001:11629: sdug gi 'brel pa la rmongs pa'i dbang gis de
NK068(nyu)001:11630: ltar spyod pa rnams r+au tra gol ba'i rgyu ste
NK068(nyu)001:11631: / de yang sngon bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol na /
NK068(nyu)001:11632: bskal pa kun tu bkod par sangs rgyas mi bskyod
NK068(nyu)001:11633: pa'i zhing mngon par dga' ba zhes bya ba'i bstan
NK068(nyu)001:11634: pa la rab tu byung ba'i dge slong thub dka'
NK068(nyu)001:11636: gang ji lta ba bzhin theg chen gyi chos 'khor bskor ba /
NK068(nyu)001:11637: thams cad nas thams cad du ma bcos ma bslad
NK068(nyu)001:11638: pa'i rnal 'byor du gnas pa skyes bu dam par
NK068(nyu)001:11639: chud pa zhig byung ba des sems can thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:11640: rgyal ba'i sras su mthong nas rtsol med kyi theg
NK068(nyu)001:11641: pa gsungs so // de'i tshe de'i na 'khor ba
NK068(nyu)001:11642: thog ma dang tha ma med par skye ba thog
NK068(nyu)001:11643: ma dang tha ma med pa'i las dang skye ba
NK068(nyu)001:11644: dpag tu med pa ni brjod kyis mi langs te
NK068(nyu)001:11645: pa gsungs so // / las skabs gcig gi skye ba cha gcig la bzung na 'di lta ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11646: de'i nye 'khor du khyim bdag ke'u ka ya zhes
NK068(nyu)001:11647: bya ba'i bu thar pa nag po zhes bya ba
NK068(nyu)001:11648: dang / de'i g.yog dan 'bag zhes bya ba gnyis
NK068(nyu)001:11649: dge slong de la dad nas de'i gan du phyin
NK068(nyu)001:11650: dang / te / thams cad ji lta bar spyod
NK068(nyu)001:11651: bzhin du lam ston pa'i thabs tshul zhus pas des
NK068(nyu)001:11652: kyang rab tu byung nas ji lta ba'i lam 'di
NK068(nyu)001:11653: dang / te / skad ces / de bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK068(nyu)001:11654: dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad kyang //
NK068(nyu)001:11655: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK068(nyu)001:11658: thar pas ni sgra ji bzhin par spyad pas lus
NK068(nyu)001:11659: dam pa'i cha byad du byas kyang sems ngan 'gro'i
NK068(nyu)001:11661: g.yog dan 'bag ni gzhi'i don gyi nges pa rnyed
NK068(nyu)001:11662: de blo gros dam par gyur nas lus ma rabs
NK068(nyu)001:11663: su gnas kyang sems dam par nges pa'i lam du
NK068(nyu)001:11664: zhugs so // de nas thar pa dpon g.yog gnyis
NK068(nyu)001:11665: lta spyod ma mthun nas rtsod pa chen por gyur
NK068(nyu)001:11666: zhugs so // te / rim bzhin slob dpon la gsol bas /
NK068(nyu)001:11667: thub dka' ni kha gsag med cing rang bzhin gsong
NK068(nyu)001:11668: por smras bas g.yog ltar nges so zhes gsungs pas
NK068(nyu)001:11669: / thar pa sems 'khrugs te slob dpon dang g.yog gnyis yul thag ring du spyugs te spangs so //
NK068(nyu)001:11670: thar pas yul khams thams cad kyang chos log par bsgyur /
NK068(nyu)001:11671: nyid kyang log par zhugs te /
NK068(nyu)001:11672: log pa'i dka' thub drag po dang brtul zhugs chen po la spyod pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11673: dur gyi mi ro blangs te kha zas su byas shing /
NK068(nyu)001:11674: lpags pa dag bshus te g.yang gzhi gyon nas /
NK068(nyu)001:11678: bya gcan gsod byed mang po brten nas thams cad srog bcad cing /
NK068(nyu)001:11679: smad 'tshong ma'i tshogs mang po bsdus te chags pa
NK068(nyu)001:11680: spyad pas dngos po bzhi las mi 'da' zhing yang
NK068(nyu)001:11681: dag pa'i don las gol bar gyur to //
NK068(nyu)001:11682: gnyis pa gol ba'i 'bras bu ji ltar smin pa la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:11683: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu sdug bsngal myong ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11684: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu gzhan la 'tshe ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11687: yi dwags su skyes tshul lo //
NK068(nyu)001:11690: srid par skye ba'i sa bon mi dge ba'i las
NK068(nyu)001:11691: rtsub mos 'phangs nas bar do med par mtshams med
NK068(nyu)001:11692: pa'i rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal ba mnar med du
NK068(nyu)001:11694: der rab tu tsha ba'i sreg pa'i sdug bsngal drag pos yun ring du gdungs pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11695: 'di bas shin tu grang yang ci ma rung snyam
NK068(nyu)001:11696: pa'i mod la kha ba dang bu yug 'tshubs pa
NK068(nyu)001:11697: sogs kyis rab tu sbrebs pas grang ba dang lus
NK068(nyu)001:11698: pad+ma ltar cher gas pa'i sdug bsngal drag po dag
NK068(nyu)001:11699: gis rab tu gdungs par byas so //
NK068(nyu)001:11700: de lta bu'i sdug bsngal rab tu tsha ba la
NK068(nyu)001:11701: sogs pa ste tsha ba nas yang sos kyi bar
NK068(nyu)001:11702: brgyad dang / shin tu grang ba pad+ma ltar cher
NK068(nyu)001:11703: gas pa la sogs pa ste chu bur can gyii
NK068(nyu)001:11704: bar brgyad po dag tu tsha grang gi dmyal ba
NK068(nyu)001:11705: phan tshun zung re re zhing skye res kyis 'jig
NK068(nyu)001:11706: rten gyi khams de 'jig pa'i dus su 'jig rten
NK068(nyu)001:11707: gyi khams gzhan dang gzhan du brgyud nas 'pho zhing
NK068(nyu)001:11708: brgyad dang / / tshe tshad ni 'jig rten gyi
NK068(nyu)001:11709: khams gcig chags gnas 'jig stong bzhi po re re
NK068(nyu)001:11710: la bar bskal nyi shu nyi shu ste bsdoms pas
NK068(nyu)001:11711: bar bskal brgyad cu la bskal chen du byas pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11712: bskal pa chen po stong phrag bcu gnyis su tsha
NK068(nyu)001:11713: grang gi sdug bsngal myong ngo //
NK068(nyu)001:11715: de nas rnam par sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:11716: de nas dmyal bar skye ba'i las kyi rnam par
NK068(nyu)001:11717: smin pa de myong stobs kyis zad pa dang yi
NK068(nyu)001:11719: ltog pa dang skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis rab tu nyen pa spyi mthun gyi sgrib pa can dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11720: phyi rol gyi 'dod pa'i dngos po rnams kyang yid
NK068(nyu)001:11721: du mi 'ong ba chu rnag tu mthong ba lta
NK068(nyu)001:11722: bu phyi'i sgrib pa can dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11723: bza' btung cung zad rnyed pa zos pa na gdug
NK068(nyu)001:11724: cing rtsub pa'i dngos po me dang khro chu sogs
NK068(nyu)001:11725: sna tshogs su 'gyur bas nang khrol sreg pa sogs
NK068(nyu)001:11727: zas skom sogs mthong bar spyod 'dod pas drung du
NK068(nyu)001:11728: bsnyegs tshe yod pa rjes tsam yang med par 'gyur
NK068(nyu)001:11729: zhing lus shin tu rid cing skam pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11730: lto ba ri bo tsam la rkang lag 'jag ma
NK068(nyu)001:11731: dang kha khab mig lta bu sogs lus dang yan
NK068(nyu)001:11732: lag dang dbang po rnams mi 'tshams pa ra nyam
NK068(nyu)001:11733: thag par gyur pa nang gi sgrib pa can zhes
NK068(nyu)001:11734: bya ste / de lta bur bskal pa chen po
NK068(nyu)001:11735: drug tu 'jig rten gyi khams brgyud cing skyes so
NK068(nyu)001:11736: bya ste / // 'di skabs kha cig na re /
NK068(nyu)001:11737: rnam par smin pa de myong bas zad dam /
NK068(nyu)001:11739: dang po ltar na yang dag pa'i lam la dgos ched med par thal /
NK068(nyu)001:11740: myong bas zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:11741: phyi ma ltar na ngan song mi khom pa'i gnas min par thal /
NK068(nyu)001:11742: mnyen po dge ba bsten du 'dug pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11744: thar pa nag pos sngon gyi las ngan rnams 'bras bu myong bas dag pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11745: phyis dpal chen po'i spyan sngar sdig pa bshags pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11747: dbang don rtogs pas dag pa yin pas gang yang 'gal ba med do snyam mo //
NK068(nyu)001:11748: gnyis pa rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu ni /
NK068(nyu)001:11749: de nas las kyi sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:11750: de nas yi dwags su skye ba'i las kyi sgrib
NK068(nyu)001:11751: pa rtsub mo'i rnam par smin pa de yang khad
NK068(nyu)001:11753: sngon bskal pa kun bkod gyi dus su khro bo dbu dang phyag mang po dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11754: phra men la sogs pa'i khro bo rang rgyud pa
NK068(nyu)001:11755: bsgoms nas drag sngags bzlas shing las barlanga por spyod
NK068(nyu)001:11756: pas srid pa'i r+au tra'i rgyud du mtshams sbyar nas
NK068(nyu)001:11757: yi dwags kyi 'gro bas bsdus pa'i las kyi srin
NK068(nyu)001:11759: de yang ji lta bu yin zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11760: yul lang ka p+au ri zhes bya bar smad 'tshong
NK068(nyu)001:11761: ma zhig gi mngal du chags te skyes nas zhag
NK068(nyu)001:11763: mi dag gis ma'i ro dang dwa phrug gnyis ka
NK068(nyu)001:11764: dug shing nal bya zhes bya ba'i rtsa bar bor
NK068(nyu)001:11765: bas / dwa bu des ma'i ro la 'jus nas
NK068(nyu)001:11766: nu ma la 'jibs pas chu ser du drangs te
NK068(nyu)001:11768: de nas khrag tu 'jibs pas zhag bdun 'tsho la /
NK068(nyu)001:11769: de nas nu ma gnyis zos pas zhag bcu'i bar 'atsho'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11770: de nas nang khrol dang sha thams cad zos pas zla ba bdun gyi bar du 'tsho zhing /
NK068(nyu)001:11771: bu de brtas par gyur nas dur khrod kyi ro rnams 'tsho ba'i bya ba byas so //
NK068(nyu)001:11772: de nas shin tu cher skyes nas ro rnams za
NK068(nyu)001:11773: zhing ro gos dang lpags pa rnams gyon te dur
NK068(nyu)001:11774: khrod kyi ma mo dang sha za yi dwags sogs
NK068(nyu)001:11775: gdug pa can rnam sha rjen pa zos pa'i mthus
NK068(nyu)001:11777: dur khrod kyi gdug pa can kun gyi bdag por
NK068(nyu)001:11778: gyur te gzhan gyi gzi byin 'phrog pa'i mi gson
NK068(nyu)001:11779: por za zhing shin tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs su gyur
NK068(nyu)001:11780: to // ma'i sha rjen par zos pas na ma
NK068(nyu)001:11781: zan ma tang ka zhes ming yongs su grags so
NK068(nyu)001:11782: to // // de yang lus rab tu 'jigs shing /
NK068(nyu)001:11783: sems gdug pa khro zhing gtum pa'i rang bzhin can /
NK068(nyu)001:11784: las kyi rdzu 'phrul lus gcig la mgo bo brgya yod pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11785: de yang mgo brnyan mi 'dra ba sna tshogs pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11786: lus mi gcig pa brgya la mgo bo gcig las med pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11787: stag seng sogs kyi lus sna tshogs su sprul pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11788: lus gcig la yan lag mang po dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11789: yan lag rigs mi 'dra ba sna tshogs pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11790: de dag gis mda' dang mda' bo che dang mdung
NK068(nyu)001:11791: thung sogs gdug pa'i lag cha sna tshogs pa thogs
NK068(nyu)001:11792: pa / lus chen po la mdog thal kha sngo
NK068(nyu)001:11793: skyar 'dug pa khrag dang zhag gi thig les brgyan
NK068(nyu)001:11794: pa / pa / thod pa'i phreng ba se ral du thogs pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11795: dmar po khrag gis bskus pa'i lpags pa bgos pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11796: thod skyogs khrag gis bkang ba rtag par 'thung ba /
NK068(nyu)001:11797: ral pa kham nag 'bar zhing snyegs pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11798: 'bru mar thod rus zas su za ba /
NK068(nyu)001:11799: ba dang kro ta an dza nas lus la brgyan la /
NK068(nyu)001:11800: bya'i gshog pa lus la byung bas nam mkha' la bya bzhin bya ba byed pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11801: gcer bu thogs pa med pa chu la nya bzhin bya ba byed pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11802: gang gis mthong bas mig rtsa rig rig dngangs shing brgyal bar byed pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11803: lus phag gi spu can rtsub la yan lag sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11804: sen mo kang ka'i mchu sder du byung bas gang zin pa'i lus brnyags par byed pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11805: sngon goms pa'i mthus lus can thams cad gsod par dmigs pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11806: 'khor rab tu mang po ste 'jig rten gyi ma
NK068(nyu)001:11807: mo dang 'byung po sogs kyis phyag byas te gtso
NK068(nyu)001:11808: bor mthong ba / gdug pa can mtha' dag g.yog dang yang g.yog tu gyur pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11809: gsod byed kyi 'khor dred mong lag rdebs dang 'phar
NK068(nyu)001:11810: ba rkang rdebs sogs bya gcan rab tu mang po
NK068(nyu)001:11811: dang / 'jigs pa'i gdug sbrul gyi gzugs dang sdom sdig sogs sna tshogs pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11812: 'jigs pa'i sgra ste nga ro ra la ra la sogs sna tshogs pa'i drag sngags sgrogs pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11814: mi snyan pa'i nga ro dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11815: mi zhim pa'i dri dang kha rlangs kyis nad rigs sna tshogs gtong zhing /
NK068(nyu)001:11816: lus can thams cad skyi bung zhes dngangs par byed pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11817: rab tu 'jigs pa'i rlung nag gis phyogs kun khebs pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11818: sna nas grang ba dang kha nas tsha ba'i dbugs
NK068(nyu)001:11819: kyis phyogs bcu kun tu stong khams thams cad 'khrugs
NK068(nyu)001:11820: par byed pa / rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa
NK068(nyu)001:11821: las gyur pa'i nad rigs bzhi brgya rtsa bzhis 'debs
NK068(nyu)001:11822: par byed pa / par byed pa / sems myos
NK068(nyu)001:11823: shing dran pa nyams par byed pa'i byed las kyi
NK068(nyu)001:11824: par byed pa / par byed pa / mthus / klu'i sde ris dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11825: lha ma yin gyi sde ris dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11827: gzugs khams las tshangs pa'i ris sogs bsam gtan dang po'i gnas gsum dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11828: 'od gsal gyi bar gnyis pa'i gsum dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11829: dge rgyas kyi bar gsum pa'i gsum dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11830: 'bras bu che ba'i bar bzhi pa'i gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:11831: gnas ris bcu gnyis pa man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK068(nyu)001:11832: 'o na gnas gtsang ma'i lha lnga mi bsdu ba ci yin zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:11833: de rnams la zag med kyi sa bon yod pa
NK068(nyu)001:11834: 'phags pa'i gnas yin pas dbang du ma 'dus gsungs
NK068(nyu)001:11835: so // gnyis pa gang gis ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:11836: gdul byar gzigs nas 'dul bar mdor bstan pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11840: de lta bu'i las kyis srin po mthu rtsal can
NK068(nyu)001:11841: de sngon dge slong thub daka'i drung du gsang sngags
NK068(nyu)001:11842: kyi theg pa chen por sems bskyed nas mos pas
NK068(nyu)001:11843: phyogs su spyad cing slob dpon thub dka' gzhon nu
NK068(nyu)001:11844: de nyid bsten pa'i stobs kyis thub dka' gzhon nu
NK068(nyu)001:11845: rdo rje sems dpar sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11846: mched dan 'bag sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'i rtsal
NK068(nyu)001:11847: chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bu gsang ba'i bdag por gyur
NK068(nyu)001:11848: pa'i thugs thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gzigs
NK068(nyu)001:11849: nas / yul dang 'phrad pa'i thugs rjes mngon spyod
NK068(nyu)001:11850: kyi phrin las kyis 'dul bar gyur pa'i dus la
NK068(nyu)001:11852: te zhes pa ni lhag ma can te 'og nas 'dul bar byeed pa dngos dang sbrel lo //
NK068(nyu)001:11854: gsang sngags kyi theg pa 'di nye lam ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK068(nyu)001:11855: thar pa nag po bskal pa dpag tu med par
NK068(nyu)001:11856: ngan song du 'khyams nas srin po'i lus blangs pa
NK068(nyu)001:11857: de srid du / dan 'bag ni rtsal chen rdzogs
NK068(nyu)001:11858: pa'i skyes bu zhes thar lam la gnas pa'i phyir
NK068(nyu)001:11859: de srid du / ro zhe na / khyab pa med de /
NK068(nyu)001:11860: 'khrul pa'i blo dus la mngon par zhen pa dag la bskal pa tshad las 'das par snang yang /
NK068(nyu)001:11861: mthar lam gyi mnyam bzhag gi dgongs pa la ltos te thun gcig las med pa'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:11862: yang na byang chub sems dpa'i dgongs spyod ni sangs
NK068(nyu)001:11863: rgyas kyis kyang dpag par dka' ba'i tshul nges don
NK068(nyu)001:11864: gyi mdo sde dag las gsungs pas log par rtog
NK068(nyu)001:11866: gnyis pa la bcu gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:11868: che mchog longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11870: sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11871: byin gyis rlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11873: sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11874: phrin las rmad du byung ba'i ngo bo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11876: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11878: ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK068(nyu)001:11880: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:11881: gdul bya bstan pa de nas 'dul byed ston pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:11882: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa sku gsung thugs che ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:11883: yon tan rdo rje gsum dang ldan pa zhi ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:11884: dkyil 'khor bkod pa'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba lha yab
NK068(nyu)001:11885: yum zung du 'brel ba'i ting nge 'dzin las /
NK068(nyu)001:11886: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis
NK068(nyu)001:11887: bdag po bdud sde'i log pa'i nga rgyal 'dul ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:11888: thabs / yang dag pa'i nga rgyal chen pos bdud zil gyis gnon pa'i gzi brjid ston pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:11889: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK068(nyu)001:11890: rdo rje'i bdag po rgyal ba kun tu bzang po
NK068(nyu)001:11891: bcom ldan 'das chos thams cad bsam gyis mi khyab
NK068(nyu)001:11892: pas dgyes pa chen po de nyid khro bo'i gtso
NK068(nyu)001:11893: bo rigs lnga he ru ka'i yang rgyal por gyur
NK068(nyu)001:11894: pa che mchog he ru ka'i sku las khro bo'i
NK068(nyu)001:11895: dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen po rnam par 'phro ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:11896: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po ting nge 'dzin la
NK068(nyu)001:11898: de yang dam pa rgyan las /
NK068(nyu)001:11899: 'dzin pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal zhing //
NK068(nyu)001:11900: gdug pa srid gsum 'dul ba yi //
NK068(nyu)001:11901: nga rgyal chen po brtan pa'i phyir //
NK068(nyu)001:11905: de bzhin nyid kyi sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:11906: chos nyid de bzhin nyid skye ba med pa'i dbyings
NK068(nyu)001:11907: nas yum khro mo dbang phyug chen mo mngon du
NK068(nyu)001:11908: phyungs te / hi hi zhes yab la dgyes shing
NK068(nyu)001:11909: tshim pa'i gad mo dang chags pa chen po'i gzi
NK068(nyu)001:11910: mdangs kyis bskul bas 'dod rgu 'byung ba rin chen
NK068(nyu)001:11911: yum gyi gsang ba'i pad+mora bde ba rgyas par mdzad
NK068(nyu)001:11912: nas yab yum gnyis su med par 'khril ba'i dgyes
NK068(nyu)001:11913: pas pad mar nor bu thim nas rol pas dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:11914: 'khor thams cad bskyed pa'i rgyur gyur pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11917: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems ye shes lnga'i sprin spros pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:11918: rkyen de'i tshe h+aum h+aum h+aum rdo rje gsum gyi bdag nyid /
NK068(nyu)001:11919: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+dala ni rdo rje khro bo sna tshogs 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK068(nyu)001:11921: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK068(nyu)001:11922: sgo gsum bkas shing gtor cig ces thugs dam bskul ba'i tshig sbyar ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11923: de skad ces brjod pas yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams
NK068(nyu)001:11924: nas khro bo 'chol ba dpag tu med pa 'phros
NK068(nyu)001:11925: pas / 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad mer mer
NK068(nyu)001:11926: shig shig tu gyur te r+au tra 'khor dang bcas
NK068(nyu)001:11927: pa zil gyis gnon cing bag khums par byed pa'o
NK068(nyu)001:11930: de yang khro bo'i sprul pa spro ba'i gnas gang
NK068(nyu)001:11931: du na 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas
NK068(nyu)001:11932: pa go mtshams med par khyab par /
NK068(nyu)001:11933: gang spro na spro ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs rnams /
NK068(nyu)001:11934: che chung ji tsam na stong gsum gyi stong chen po 'jig rten gyi khams tsam /
NK068(nyu)001:11935: mang nyung gi tshad ji tsam na phyogs bcu'i 'jig
NK068(nyu)001:11936: rten gyi rdul phra mo snyed tsam 'thon pas stong
NK068(nyu)001:11937: khams gang bar gyur nas gdug pa can rnams bag
NK068(nyu)001:11941: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs de dag spros pas
NK068(nyu)001:11942: phyi ltar 'jig rten drug gi phyogs thams cad rnam
NK068(nyu)001:11944: tshabs che bas rab tu g.yos /
NK068(nyu)001:11945: khyab cing tshabs che bas kun tu g.yos so //
NK068(nyu)001:11946: nang ltar de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la g.yo thob goms pa'i nyams gsum bogs thon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11947: phyi ltar na zin pa'i sgra thams cad drag por 'ur 'ur /
NK068(nyu)001:11950: nang ltar na kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin la bogs gsum thon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11951: phyi ltar na ma zin pa'i sgra rnams kyang rang khrol du chem chem /
NK068(nyu)001:11954: nang ltar na phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bogs gsum thon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11955: phyi ltar na ri gling sogs dum bur shig shig /
NK068(nyu)001:11958: nang ltar na phyag rgya spros bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin la bogs gsum thon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11959: phyi ltar na de dag kyang gtor gtor /
NK068(nyu)001:11962: nang ltar na tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi ting nge 'dzin la bogs gsum thon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:11965: de ltar ltas chen po bco lnga dang khro bo'i
NK068(nyu)001:11966: sprin tshogs pa mi zad pa'i chos kun tu snang
NK068(nyu)001:11967: ba de'i tshe 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i stong
NK068(nyu)001:11968: gsum gyi khams thams cad na gnas pa'i nag phyogs
NK068(nyu)001:11969: kyi gtso bo / so so'i gnas su dbang che ba ma h+aa de ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11970: 'phrul dang gzi brjid che ba tshangs pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11971: nus mthu che ba'i lha khyab 'jug dang /
NK068(nyu)001:11973: mchod par 'os pa'i gnas brgya byin la sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:11974: dregs pa can thams cad khams 'khrugs nas dran pa nyams shing brgyal /
NK068(nyu)001:11975: lus sa la 'gyel zhing rab tu brgyal /
NK068(nyu)001:11976: sems myos shing kun tu brgyal bar gyur to //
NK068(nyu)001:11979: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul bstan pa de nas bcom
NK068(nyu)001:11980: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po che mchog he ru
NK068(nyu)001:11981: ka de nyid 'jigs byed chen po zhal shin tu
NK068(nyu)001:11982: rngams pa bdud dang log 'dren thams cad sngangs shing
NK068(nyu)001:11983: skyi bung zhes byed pa'i ye shes kyi gzi brjid
NK068(nyu)001:11984: me dpung 'bar ba chen po'i klong na /
NK068(nyu)001:11985: 'dod chags zad par byed pa'i rtags su khrag 'thung zhing /
NK068(nyu)001:11986: dbang drag gi las mthar phyin pa'i rtags su sku mdog smug nag /
NK068(nyu)001:11987: gdul bya 'dul thabs gcig tu ma nges pa'i rtags su cir yang 'gyur ba'i rnam pa can /
NK068(nyu)001:11988: dbu dang phyag dang zhabs stong gsum gyi rdul snyed ltar tshad bzung du med pa mtha' yas pa /
NK068(nyu)001:11989: phyag rnams na mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa gcig tu gyur pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:11990: gong du khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dpag tu med pa spros pa de dag las /
NK068(nyu)001:11991: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes las 'phros pa'i phyir
NK068(nyu)001:11992: khro bo thams cad che mchog he ru ka de
NK068(nyu)001:11993: nyid la 'dus te badz+ra he ru kar gyur pa
NK068(nyu)001:11994: ni / rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dbu gsum /
NK068(nyu)001:11995: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug /
NK068(nyu)001:11996: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su zhabs bzhi par gyur te /
NK068(nyu)001:11997: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang chen por bzhugs par dgyes nas /
NK068(nyu)001:11998: mkha' rlung gi dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i 'dod chags
NK068(nyu)001:11999: ma spangs pa'i rtags su khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:12000: na / zhe sdang ma spangs pa'i rtags su keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi steng /
NK068(nyu)001:12001: ye shes chen po'i lta ngan sbyangs pa'i rtags su
NK068(nyu)001:12002: ye shes kyi me ri me dpung 'bar ba chen
NK068(nyu)001:12004: gzhal yas khang gi dbus kyi lte ba la mdzad
NK068(nyu)001:12005: pa mthar phyin pa'i rtags su dbang phyug chen po
NK068(nyu)001:12007: dur khrod kyi bdag po dregs pa chen po r+au
NK068(nyu)001:12008: tra pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba'i gdan la
NK068(nyu)001:12009: zhabs g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum du bzhugs so //
NK068(nyu)001:12010: de bzhin du bde gshegs rigs dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12013: las kyi rigs kyi khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin
NK068(nyu)001:12014: phung de dag kyang so sor 'dus pa la me
NK068(nyu)001:12015: long lta bu la sogs pa ye shes bzhi'i bdag
NK068(nyu)001:12016: nyid rigs bzhi'i he ru kar gyur pa'ang /
NK068(nyu)001:12017: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po bud+d+ha he ru kar gyur te 'khor lo'i shar phyogs dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12018: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po cher gyur te lho phyogs su dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12019: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad+mara gyur te nub phyogs su dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12020: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las su gyur te byang phyoogs su bzhugs so //
NK068(nyu)001:12021: khrag 'thung rigs lnga po de dag kun kyang 'jigs
NK068(nyu)001:12022: byed chen po'i cha lugs dur khrod kyi chas dang
NK068(nyu)001:12023: / zhal nas h+aum phata sogs gsung rngams pa'i nga
NK068(nyu)001:12024: ro dang bcas pas me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na
NK068(nyu)001:12025: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis shar du dri za
NK068(nyu)001:12026: / dang / byang du gnod sbyin dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12028: lhor gshin rje la sogs pa khyo shug ste pho kha sbubs dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12029: mo gan rkyal gyi gdan la zhabs g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum du bzhugs so //
NK068(nyu)001:12030: btsun mo khrag 'thung chen mo rigs lnga'i tshogs rnams
NK068(nyu)001:12031: kyang rigs so so'i he ru ka'i sku la 'khril
NK068(nyu)001:12034: de nas dregs pa sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:12035: sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang
NK068(nyu)001:12036: bas dregs pa can gdan du byas pa de nas
NK068(nyu)001:12037: dregs pa chen po r+au tra la sogs pa pho
NK068(nyu)001:12038: rgyud rnams kyis zhe sdang gis khro zhing gtum pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:12039: sems kyis dgra zlar mthong ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12040: lus gdan du gnas kyang gdug pa'i rdzu 'phrul chen
NK068(nyu)001:12041: po sna tshogs bstan nas 'khor rnams dang skad mthun
NK068(nyu)001:12042: par mgrin gcig tu gdug pa'i nga ros ngag mi
NK068(nyu)001:12043: snyan pa barlanga po'i gtum tshig gis 'di skad du
NK068(nyu)001:12044: smras pa / nged rnams gdan du bcings pa las thong thong /
NK068(nyu)001:12045: khyed rnams snying rje'i bdag po ma yin nam /
NK068(nyu)001:12046: ci bdag cag la tho 'tshams par byed dam /
NK068(nyu)001:12048: shin tu gdug pa'i sems kyis khros nas da dung rngam mo //
NK068(nyu)001:12049: de nas gdug pa can de dag gi gnyen por
NK068(nyu)001:12050: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po rigs lnga'i he
NK068(nyu)001:12051: ru ka nyid sgrol byed rdo rje srin po he
NK068(nyu)001:12052: ru ka klong dgu rngams pa'i zhal du gdug pa
NK068(nyu)001:12053: can gsol ba'i rtags su dbu dgu /
NK068(nyu)001:12054: sgrol byed kyi ging bco brgyad kyis gdug pa can sgrol ba'i rtags su phyag bco brgyad /
NK068(nyu)001:12055: tshad med bzhi dang phrin las bzhis don mdzad pa'i rtags su zhabs brgyad du gnas par sprul nas /
NK068(nyu)001:12056: thugs rjes 'dul ba'i thabs la mkhas pa nyid kyis
NK068(nyu)001:12057: r+au tra'i ngor shin tu khros pa ltar snang nas
NK068(nyu)001:12059: h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes de dag gi sgo gsum bsdus shig pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12060: ha ha ha zhes dug gsum zhal du gsol bar dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12061: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi zhes sha khrag rus gsum zo zhig pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12062: sngags de skad ces brjod pas dbang phyug chen po
NK068(nyu)001:12063: la sogs pa gdug pa chen po'i tshogs de dag
NK068(nyu)001:12064: gi bdag 'dzin gcod phyir don snying dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12065: yul 'dzin gyi sgo 'gag phyir dbang po kun phyung /
NK068(nyu)001:12066: mngon zhen dgag phyir nang khrol kun drangs /
NK068(nyu)001:12067: las ngan gyi bag chags gcod phyir yan lag kun dum bur bcad cing gtubs nas /
NK068(nyu)001:12068: dug gsum dag par mdzad pa'i phyir du gti mug sha kun zos /
NK068(nyu)001:12070: zhe sdang rus pa kun 'chos te ming tsam med par mdzad pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12073: de ltar gtso bo r+au tra la sogs pa pho
NK068(nyu)001:12074: rnams bsgral te btul ba de nas mo rnams sbyor
NK068(nyu)001:12076: h+aum h+aum h+aum ni lus ngag yid gsum sdus shig pa'i bskul tshig /
NK068(nyu)001:12077: b+h+yo ni ma mo rnams snying po dang bod pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12081: de skad ces brjod pas phyogs bcu'i snod kyi 'jig
NK068(nyu)001:12082: rten gyi khams nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa dang bcas
NK068(nyu)001:12083: pa kun ma lus par yungs 'bru gcig tsam du
NK068(nyu)001:12084: chud par dbang 'byor ba'i rdzu 'phrul chen pos bsdus
NK068(nyu)001:12085: so // de nas bcud kyi sems can 'byung po
NK068(nyu)001:12086: phal pa'i rigs ma lus pa'i rgyal po ni lha
NK068(nyu)001:12087: dang lha min blon po chen po rnams yin la
NK068(nyu)001:12088: so // / de'i yang rgyal po ni dregs pa
NK068(nyu)001:12089: chen po srin po la sogs pa dbang phyug chen
NK068(nyu)001:12090: po pho rgyud nyi shu rtsa brgyad po yin pas
NK068(nyu)001:12091: so // / / de rnams so so'i chung ma
NK068(nyu)001:12092: ni 'byung po mo rgyud phal pa'i rigs thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:12093: kyi rje mo ste blon po chen po'i chung ma
NK068(nyu)001:12094: de tsho'i yang rje mor gyur pa dbang phyug ma
NK068(nyu)001:12096: khyo'i ming chung mar grags pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12097: de yang shar gyi ma mo drug ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12098: srin po da sha g+r+ai ba'i chung ma srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12099: lha tshangs pa'i chung ma tshangs ma dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12100: lha chen drag po'i chung ma 'khrug mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12101: brgya byin gyi chung ma dbang mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12102: khyab 'jug gi chung ma 'jug sred mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12103: gzhon nu gdong drug gi chung ma gzhon nu mo dang drug go //
NK068(nyu)001:12105: 'jug sred kyi chung ma dmar mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12106: lha'i bu nyi ma'i chung ma bdud rtsi mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12107: zla ba'i chung ma zhi ba mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12108: be con gyi chung ma be con mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12109: srin po skya rengs khrag mig gi chung ma srin mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12110: lha za byed kyi chung ma za ba mo dang drug go //
NK068(nyu)001:12111: nub kyii ma mo drug ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12112: dga' byed dbang phyug gi chung ma dga' ba mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12113: stobs bzang gi chung ma ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12114: b+h+rim gi ri ti'i chung ma gcig pur spyod ma dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12115: 'dod lha'i chung ma yid 'phrog ma dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12116: nor srung gi chung ma grub pa mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12117: rlung lha'i chung ma rlung mo dang drug go //
NK068(nyu)001:12118: byang gi ma mo drug ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12119: lha gsod byed kyi chung ma gsod byed mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12120: me lha'i chung ma me mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12121: sa bdag phag chen gyi chung ma phag mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12122: gshin rje'i chung ma rgan byed mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12123: bi na ya ka'i chung ma sna chen mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12124: chu lha'i chung ma chu lha mo dang drug go //
NK068(nyu)001:12126: lha nag po chen po'i chung ma nag mo chen mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12127: ra gdong chen po'i chung ma ra mgo dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12128: srin po bum sna'i chung ma bum sna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12129: lha gsus po che'i chung ma gsus 'dzin ser nag chen mo bzhi'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12130: de la sogs pa ma mo'i tshogs las byed pa bran dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12131: de'i yang las byed pa yang bran dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12132: bkur sti byed pa'i g.yog dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12133: de la yang bskur sti byed pa g.yang g.yog dang
NK068(nyu)001:12134: bcas pa'i 'khor zhing gi rdul ltar mtha' yas pa
NK068(nyu)001:12135: thams cad kyang chags pa chen pos dbang du bsdus
NK068(nyu)001:12137: de nas bcom ldan 'das sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:12138: mo rgyud rnams bsdus pa de nas bcom ldan 'das
NK068(nyu)001:12139: dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo
NK068(nyu)001:12140: rje srin por snang ba des ma mo rnams 'dul
NK068(nyu)001:12141: ba'i thabs kyis / slar yang rigs lnga'i 'jigs byed
NK068(nyu)001:12142: he ru ka chen po lnga ka yongs su rdzogs
NK068(nyu)001:12143: par ma mo rnams kyi ngo la snang bar byas
NK068(nyu)001:12144: ba'i thabs kyis / nas / rigs lnga de dag
NK068(nyu)001:12145: kun kyang thabs shes gnyis su med par dgyes par
NK068(nyu)001:12146: rol pa'i byang sems las gnas yul sgo ma'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:12147: 'khor gyi tshogs sprin 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting
NK068(nyu)001:12148: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK068(nyu)001:12149: sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed ba'i rdo rje las sngags 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK068(nyu)001:12151: badz+ra ni rdo rje ste yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje /
NK068(nyu)001:12152: pra be sha rab tu zhugs pa ste yum gyi gsang ba'i pad+mora /
NK068(nyu)001:12153: a la la hohdagyesa pa'i ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12156: de skad ces brjod pas 'byung mo'i rgyal mo rnams
NK068(nyu)001:12157: rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang ba la shin tu
NK068(nyu)001:12158: chags pa'i yid rab tu g.yos nas /
NK068(nyu)001:12159: rang rang gi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor rdo rje sdud pa ste 'dzum zhing rgyas par gyur nas /
NK068(nyu)001:12160: dper na rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul
NK068(nyu)001:12161: du dbang phyug mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad rnams bcom
NK068(nyu)001:12162: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung rigs
NK068(nyu)001:12164: 'di ltar dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo rje he ru ka'i sku brgyad du snang ba la /
NK068(nyu)001:12165: phyogs kyi gtso mo srin mo chen mo'i srin mo sogs bzhi dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12166: sgo skyong nag mo chen mo sogs bzhi ste brgyad po rnams so sor 'khril to //
NK068(nyu)001:12167: bcom ldan 'das khrag 'thung chen po rigs bzhi po lnga lngar snang ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12168: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la tshangs ma sogs shar phyogs kyi ma mo lnga rnams 'khril to //
NK068(nyu)001:12169: rin po che'i sku la bdud rtsi mo sogs lho'i ma mo lnga rnams 'khril to //
NK068(nyu)001:12170: pad+ma'i sku la khrag gis myos ma sogs nub kyi ma mo lnga rnams 'khril to //
NK068(nyu)001:12171: kun tu las kyi sku la me mo sogs byang gi ma mo lnga rnams 'khril to //
NK068(nyu)001:12172: de la kha cig na re /
NK068(nyu)001:12173: 'o na de dag dang res mos su rol lam /
NK068(nyu)001:12174: dus gcig tu rol zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:12176: khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i snang ba la sbyor ba'i rtog pa mi mnga' la /
NK068(nyu)001:12177: ma mo'i snang ba la de bzhin gshegs pa re res sbyor bar snang ba ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12179: ma mo yang de bzhin gshegs pa re re dang sbyor ba mthong ba ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12181: des na nag phyogs kyi chung ma phal pa dang
NK068(nyu)001:12182: yang bran sogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i snang ngor
NK068(nyu)001:12183: yang khrag 'thung dpa' bo'i rnam pa bsam gyis mi
NK068(nyu)001:12184: khyab par snang nas sbyor ba mdzad pa shes par
NK068(nyu)001:12185: bya'o // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen
NK068(nyu)001:12186: po rigs lnga'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag gis
NK068(nyu)001:12187: h+aum zhes brjod pas dbang mo rnams kyi pad+ma'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:12188: 'khor gyi tshogs rigs lnga'i rdo rje la bsdus nas
NK068(nyu)001:12189: sku'i stod smad shin tu bcums pas rol par gyur
NK068(nyu)001:12190: bya'o // to // bcu gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12193: sgo ma rnams spro ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12197: yab yum gnyis med du rol pa de nas dgyes
NK068(nyu)001:12198: te ha zhes brjod pa'i bzhad sgras sbyoor mtshams nas
NK068(nyu)001:12199: yab yum gyi byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK068(nyu)001:12200: dkar mo'i tshogs koo r+ai mas zhi ba'i las dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12201: rkun mo'i tshogs tsoo r+ai mas dbang gi las dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12202: rmongs mo'i tshogs pra mo has zhi ba'i las dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12203: thal byed ma'i tshogs be ta l+ais drag po'i las dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12204: sbos mo'i tshogs puk+ka s+ais rgyas pa'i las dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12205: gtum mo'i tshogs g+hasma r+ais drag po'i las dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12206: sme sha can gyi tshogs sme sha n+ais las gang 'dod dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12207: ma tshogs ma'i tshogs tsan+da l+ais 'phel ba'i las grub pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12208: de rnams kyis zhing dbyug dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12209: thod khrag sogs rang rang gi lag cha dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12210: rngam zhing brjid pa'i rgyan chas dang ldan pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12211: ngo mtshar ba'i gzugs rgyan dang bcas pas dbang mo'i mkha' nas phyir 'thon to //
NK068(nyu)001:12212: gnas ma brgyad po re re yang nyi shu rtsa
NK068(nyu)001:12213: brgyad du 'thon nas kyang rigs bsdus te 'bar ba
NK068(nyu)001:12214: chen po'i 'khor lo'i rtsibs mchan dang gru chad bzhi
NK068(nyu)001:12215: shar lho'i phyogs nas g.yas bskor gyis 'khor bar za
NK068(nyu)001:12216: za 'cha' 'cha' 'dra ba 'jigs pa'i gzugs don rtags
NK068(nyu)001:12217: dang mthun par rang rang gi lag cha dang bcas
NK068(nyu)001:12220: gnas ma brgyad 'thon pa de nas slar yang shin
NK068(nyu)001:12221: tu dgyes nas he zhes brjod pa'i bzhad sgra dang
NK068(nyu)001:12222: sbyor mtshams byang chub sems kyi sprin las yul ma
NK068(nyu)001:12223: brgyad 'thon te / de yang thams cad zil gyis gnon pa seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12224: dpa' rtul gyis drag po'i las byed pa stag gdong dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12225: thabs la mkhas pas phung po'i bdud dag par bya pa wa gdong dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12226: mel tshe mkhas shing lha'i bu'i bdud 'joms par byed pa khyi gdong dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12227: mig rno zhing shes bya la thogs pa med pa bzhad gdong dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12228: dbugs bral la spyod cing 'khor ba dang du len
NK068(nyu)001:12229: pas 'chi bdag gi bdud 'joms pa kang+ka'i gdong dang
NK068(nyu)001:12230: / nyon mongs pa zad par byed pa khwa gdong dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12231: gdul bya phra ba'ang mi 'dor ba 'ug gdong chen mo'i tshogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:12232: de ltar phra men chen mo re re'ang nyer brgyad kyi tshogs dang bcas pa rnams /
NK068(nyu)001:12233: lag gnyis gyen du bsnol bas ro bzung ba sogs
NK068(nyu)001:12234: rang rang gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar du ma
NK068(nyu)001:12235: dang bcas mkha' nas 'thon par gyur to //
NK068(nyu)001:12236: 'thon nas kyang rigs bsdus te 'bar ba chen po'i
NK068(nyu)001:12237: 'khor lo'i phyi rol gser khyams la shar phyogs nas
NK068(nyu)001:12238: 'khor bar phyogs bzhir mche ba can bzhi dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12239: mtshams bzhir gshog pa can bzhi rngams pa'i mdangs kyis 'khod do //
NK068(nyu)001:12242: yul ma brgyad 'thon pa de nas shin tu dgyes
NK068(nyu)001:12243: pas phrin las bzhi'i snang bas phyogs bcu'i zhing khams
NK068(nyu)001:12244: ma lus par khyab nas phata ces brjod pa'i bzhad
NK068(nyu)001:12245: sgra dang byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK068(nyu)001:12247: 'khor bar mi gtong ba rdo rje sring 'gro rta gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12248: snying rjes 'ching ba phrin las gcig tu 'jug pa rdo rje gdong mo phag gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12249: dga' bas sdom pa rdo rje 'jig rten seng gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12250: btang snyoms kyis myos par byed pa rdo rje ro
NK068(nyu)001:12251: langs spyang gdong ma'i tshogs rnams lcags kyu sogs rang
NK068(nyu)001:12252: rang gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar du ma bcas
NK068(nyu)001:12254: 'thon nas kyang nyer brgyad po rigs bsdus te 'bar
NK068(nyu)001:12255: ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgo bzhir shin tu
NK068(nyu)001:12256: rngams pa'i gzugs kyis gnas so //
NK068(nyu)001:12257: 'dir sras kyi dkyil 'khor gnas yul sgo ma 'di
NK068(nyu)001:12258: rnams dbang mo dang rol pa las bskyed pa dang
NK068(nyu)001:12259: / sgrub thabs nas rigs kyi yum dang rol pa
NK068(nyu)001:12260: las bskyed par 'dod pa gnyis 'gal lo zhe na
NK068(nyu)001:12262: 'dir dregs pa can bsgral zhing de'i 'khor mo rnams
NK068(nyu)001:12263: dbang du bsdus te sbyor ba ni thabs chen po'i
NK068(nyu)001:12264: sbyor sgrol gyi che ba dbyung ba'i dgos pa yod
NK068(nyu)001:12265: pa'i phyir dbang mo dang rol la /
NK068(nyu)001:12266: don gyis 'dir yang ye shes kyi yum dang rol pa shes dgos te /
NK068(nyu)001:12268: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas /
NK068(nyu)001:12269: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:12270: yang 'dir dbang mo nyer brgyad la bu mo nyi
NK068(nyu)001:12271: shu las ma byung ba ni nyung bar 'gyur ro
NK068(nyu)001:12273: tshogs dang bcas pa mi'i dbang du na re re yang nyer brgyad nyer brgyad de /
NK068(nyu)001:12274: brgya phrag lnga dang bcu phrag drug yod la /
NK068(nyu)001:12275: dkyil 'khor du 'god pa'i tshe de dag thugs ye
NK068(nyu)001:12276: shes su gcig pa'i phyir re rer bsdus nas 'god
NK068(nyu)001:12280: dkyil 'khor 'god pa'i mdzad pa rdzogs pa de nas
NK068(nyu)001:12281: yab yum dgyes pa chen po'i byang chub sems kyi
NK068(nyu)001:12282: sprin las phyogs bcu nas phata ces bsgrags pas khro
NK068(nyu)001:12283: mo thams cad shin tu yang khros nas /
NK068(nyu)001:12284: las las grub pa'i ma mo thams cad kyang rang
NK068(nyu)001:12285: rang gi gnas shar phyogs la sogs pa ga la
NK068(nyu)001:12286: ba der yud tsam la rdzu 'phrul gyis phyin par
NK068(nyu)001:12287: las la bakye'o // gsum pa de ltar btul ba'i 'bras bu la bzhi ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12288: dbang bskur te gnas spar nas snang 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin thob pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12289: 'bangs su dam bcus nas lus gdan du phul ba /
NK068(nyu)001:12290: 'khor phul te gus pas mchod par dam bcas pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12291: dbang mo rnams las nod pa la dbang bskur nas mu ran la bkod tshul lo //
NK068(nyu)001:12293: de nas bcom ldan 'das sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:12294: sbyor sgrol gyi phrin las rmad du byung ba bstan
NK068(nyu)001:12295: pa de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po
NK068(nyu)001:12296: dpal khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga po de dag
NK068(nyu)001:12297: kun badz+ra he ru kar bsdus pa nyid rang byung
NK068(nyu)001:12298: gi thugs rje chen pos gso bar byed pas bdud
NK068(nyu)001:12299: rtsi 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK068(nyu)001:12300: snyoms par zhugs nas sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer
NK068(nyu)001:12301: mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las dbang bskur ba'i dam
NK068(nyu)001:12302: rdzas sngags dang bcas pa 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK068(nyu)001:12303: de yang sngar dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:12304: dregs pa can rnams kyis yan lag kun bcad gtub
NK068(nyu)001:12308: bcom ldan 'das khro bo chen po de dag gi
NK068(nyu)001:12309: lto ba chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na yod
NK068(nyu)001:12310: pa dpal chen po'i snams te bshang lam nas bton
NK068(nyu)001:12311: te mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyi rgya mtshor chud pa
NK068(nyu)001:12312: las / slar yang snams nas u tsush+ma kro ta zhes pas khro bo sme ba brtsegs pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12313: dam rdzas bdud rtsi phyungs nas /
NK068(nyu)001:12314: badz+ra ma h+aa a mri ta mchog ster rdo rje bdud rtsi chen po /
NK068(nyu)001:12315: ma h+aa kro d+ha khro bo chen po /
NK068(nyu)001:12316: am am am zhes brjod pas lan gsum du dam rdzas bdud rtsi lcer bzhag cing dbang bskur /
NK068(nyu)001:12317: sme ba brtsegs pas 'dam kun 'thungs te gsol bas /
NK068(nyu)001:12318: dbang thob pa'i byin rlabs kyis dregs pa can de
NK068(nyu)001:12319: dag dran pa slar rnyed nas rtog tshogs thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:12320: sku dang ye shes su gsal bar gyur to //
NK068(nyu)001:12321: de'i tshe snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting 'dzin
NK068(nyu)001:12322: thob pas 'bar ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs
NK068(nyu)001:12323: bsam yas lhun grub kyi zhal mngon sum du mthong
NK068(nyu)001:12324: ste / khro bo de dag thams cad kyang dbu dgu brgya pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12327: sku gzi byin mtha' yas pa 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor na bzhugs par mthong ngo //
NK068(nyu)001:12328: ye shes kyi cho 'phrul gyis sprul pa'i r+au tra btul ba de'i dus su /
NK068(nyu)001:12329: gdul bar bya ba'i yul 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK068(nyu)001:12330: bcur srid pa gsum po kun tu gnas shing dbang
NK068(nyu)001:12331: bsgyur ba'i dregs pa'i dbang phyug chen po thams cad
NK068(nyu)001:12332: gang la gang gis ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs kyi
NK068(nyu)001:12333: sgo sna tshogs su snang ba'i rol pa bsam gyis
NK068(nyu)001:12334: mi khyab par rang rang gi zhing so sor snang
NK068(nyu)001:12335: bas snga phyi med par dus gcig tu brtul lo
NK068(nyu)001:12337: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK068(nyu)001:12338: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub //
NK068(nyu)001:12340: gzhan yang gsang ba'i 'og min du ston 'khor tshogs
NK068(nyu)001:12341: nas snying ga'i 'og min du sangs rgyas pa'i tshe
NK068(nyu)001:12342: khu rdul rlung gsum rnam shes dang bcas pa'i dri
NK068(nyu)001:12343: ma cha phra ba de nyid bcom pa'i rtsal snang
NK068(nyu)001:12344: phyi rol du zhi khro'i gleng gzhir snang ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12345: dgos ched ni ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag chos mig
NK068(nyu)001:12346: dang ldan pa rnams rgyud 'di lta bu'i r+au trar
NK068(nyu)001:12347: gol ba'i gol sa bkag pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12348: khyad par du lam pa rnams kyis rdzogs rim gyi
NK068(nyu)001:12349: dus sbyor can gyi rtsa dang las rlung gi rgyu
NK068(nyu)001:12350: ba bcom nas ye shes kyi rtsa rlung khyad par
NK068(nyu)001:12351: can la dkri ba'i ched du'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12353: r+au tra de sprul pa ba yin nam /
NK068(nyu)001:12355: snga ma ltar na ngan song gi sdug bsngal myong bas bshad pas rigs pa ma yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:12356: phyi ma ltar na yi dwags kyi srin po chen po zer bas 'dod khams pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:12357: des gzugs khams dbang du bsdus pa mi 'thad de /
NK068(nyu)001:12358: der bgrod pa la bsam gtan gyi ting nge 'dzin thob dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12359: dpal chen po dang spyod yul gcig tu ma spyad pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:12360: zhal mthong ba dngos kyi gdul byar gyur pa'i mi 'thad do zer na /
NK068(nyu)001:12362: sems can gyi don du de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul
NK068(nyu)001:12363: pa tha mal pa'i gzugs su snang ba rnams chos
NK068(nyu)001:12364: can / khyod tha mal par thal /
NK068(nyu)001:12366: 'dod pa'i rten can gyi 'phags pa chos can /
NK068(nyu)001:12367: khyod kyis gzugs khams dbang du bsdu mi nus par thal /
NK068(nyu)001:12368: khyod 'dod pa'i rten can yin pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:12371: skye bo ma rig gis ldongs pas //
NK068(nyu)001:12372: srid rtse'i bar du song nas kyang //
NK068(nyu)001:12373: zhes pa'i lung gis gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK068(nyu)001:12374: yang sh+aakya thub pa mthong ba'i sems can rnams chos can /
NK068(nyu)001:12375: khyod thub pa dang spyod yul gcig tu spyad par thal /
NK068(nyu)001:12376: de'i phyir rtags khas blangs la /
NK068(nyu)001:12377: de ltar yang 'grel pa lung bstan las /
NK068(nyu)001:12378: ji skad bshad pa'i mthu 'di dag rang rgyud pa la yod pa ma yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:12379: sprul pa yin par som nyi mi bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12381: de ltar na gong du bdag tu rmongs pa'i zhes sogs kyis gnod do zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:12383: phyis 'jig rten du cha lugs dang mthu cha 'dra
NK068(nyu)001:12384: ba'i r+au tra rang mtshan pa 'byung ba rnams rgyu
NK068(nyu)001:12385: de lta bus bskyed par ston pa'i phyir dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12386: der ma zad gnyen po mchog rnams nyes pas mi gos par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:12387: rgyal bas sor mo'i phreng ba can sprul nas btul ba bzhin thabs kyi che ba dbyung ba dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12388: sngags lam pa'i gol sa dgag pa'i ched du thabs la mkhas pa'i cho 'phrul rmad du byung ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12390: de nas de dag sogs te /
NK068(nyu)001:12391: gnas spar ba de nas dregs pa can de dag shin tu skrag pas lus shin tu 'dar shing /
NK068(nyu)001:12392: sems bred pas rab tu dpa' zhum pa'i nga ros /
NK068(nyu)001:12393: bdag cag khyed kyi 'bangs su mchi /
NK068(nyu)001:12395: gal te 'bangs su nan tan ma bgyis na /
NK068(nyu)001:12396: bdag can rnams kyi mgo dang lus ni dum bu brgyar 'gas shing /
NK068(nyu)001:12397: snying yang tshal pa stong du 'gas shing dum bur gtub par gyis shig /
NK068(nyu)001:12398: lus kyang rul zhing myags la dmod tshig gi mes tshig nas thal bar brlag pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12399: tshe phyi mar yang rdo rje'i dmyal bar lhung nas 'o dod chen po 'bod par shog /
NK068(nyu)001:12400: de skad ces 'bangs su mchi bar mna' bor nas
NK068(nyu)001:12401: rang rang gi lus khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK068(nyu)001:12402: gyi gdan du phul nas bzhag go //
NK068(nyu)001:12405: dregs pa'i bdag po thams cad kyis ngag mthun par
NK068(nyu)001:12406: mgrin gcig tu lus phul nas yang 'khor 'bul ba
NK068(nyu)001:12407: smras pa / bdag cag rnams kyi mchis brang chung ma dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12409: sring mo rnams kyang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor chen po la 'bul bas bzhes su gsol /
NK068(nyu)001:12410: gang gis na gdug pa can 'dul ba la nyam
NK068(nyu)001:12411: nga ba med pas dpa' bo lha chen rnams kyi
NK068(nyu)001:12412: yang rje bor gyur pa dpal he ru kas bzhes
NK068(nyu)001:12414: phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi dgongs pa bsgrub par dam bca' ba ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12415: gdug pa can bdag cag so so'i 'khor dang bcas
NK068(nyu)001:12416: pa rnams kyis khro bo'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen
NK068(nyu)001:12417: po 'di'i don zab mo rtogs pa rnams lta ci
NK068(nyu)001:12418: smos / tha na ming tsam mos gus kyis 'dzin
NK068(nyu)001:12419: par byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa de yang dper na
NK068(nyu)001:12420: lha'i dbang po dang klu'i dbang po'i gtsug tor nor
NK068(nyu)001:12421: bu rin po che 'od 'bar ba de lha bran
NK068(nyu)001:12422: dang klu bran rnams kyis mthong ma thag tu phyag
NK068(nyu)001:12423: ma byas na mgo bo 'gas pas mi bkur ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:12424: thabs med pa ltar sems la g.yo sgyu med cing
NK068(nyu)001:12425: gus pa dang ldan pa'i sems kyis blangs te spyi
NK068(nyu)001:12426: bo'i gtsug tu bzhag nas bkur bar bagyi'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12427: de yang 'khur lugs gsum dang mthong lugs bzhi ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12428: rab lta ba dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa gtsug gi nor bu ltar mthong zhing 'khur /
NK068(nyu)001:12429: 'bring ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa rje dpon dbang po che ltar mthong zhing 'khur /
NK068(nyu)001:12430: tha ma spyod lam da ngaldana pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK068(nyu)001:12431: de spyan 'dren ngo chen ltar du mthong zhing 'khur
NK068(nyu)001:12432: la / yang tha dam la mi gnas pa'i rnal
NK068(nyu)001:12433: 'byor pa ni bka' chad kyi gnas su mthong zhing
NK068(nyu)001:12434: 'khur ba lta ga la srid do //
NK068(nyu)001:12435: zhes sngon gyi bla ma rnams kyis gsungs so //
NK068(nyu)001:12436: des na dam la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pa de'i
NK068(nyu)001:12437: dgos pa ci yang rung ba ma lus pa rdzogs
NK068(nyu)001:12438: par bdag cag rnams kyis bsgrub bo //
NK068(nyu)001:12439: gal te dpa' bo dpal chen he ru ka'i spyan sngar 'dir smras pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12440: khas blangs bzhin du ma bsgrubs na /
NK068(nyu)001:12441: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo bo bkas /
NK068(nyu)001:12443: snying tshal par gyur nas rul bar mchi'o zhes gna' bor ba'i tshig de dag smras so //
NK068(nyu)001:12444: de ltar du r+au tra 'khor bcas kyi dam bcas pa bzhin bsgrub cing lam nyams su blangs so //
NK068(nyu)001:12445: de'i gtso bo thar pa nag po da lta'i bskal
NK068(nyu)001:12446: pa 'di'i yun du dge bsnyen legs ldan nag po
NK068(nyu)001:12447: zhes bya bar gyur nas rnal 'byor pa'i chos srung
NK068(nyu)001:12448: bar byed la / bskal pa phyi ma la 'og
NK068(nyu)001:12449: gi phyogs kyi 'jig rten thal bas khebs pa zhes
NK068(nyu)001:12450: bya bar sangs rgyas thal ba'i dbang po'i dbyangs zhes
NK068(nyu)001:12451: bya bar 'tshang rgya bar lung bstan to //
NK068(nyu)001:12454: bro bor ba de nas dregs pa can de dag gi chung ma'i tshogs dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12456: ma dang bu mo'i tshogs thams cad sngar bkye ba
NK068(nyu)001:12457: las slar yang dkyil 'khor gyi drung du yud tsam
NK068(nyu)001:12458: gyis 'ongs nas / de thams cad kyis ngag mthun par mgrin gcig tu smras pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12459: bdag cag dbang mo 'khor tshogs thams cad kyang dpa' bo chen po'i 'bangs su mchi'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12460: dpa' bo chen pos bdag cag rnams la zhi rgyas
NK068(nyu)001:12461: dbang drag gi las thams cad 'grub pa'i phrin las
NK068(nyu)001:12462: kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol zhes smras so //
NK068(nyu)001:12463: ci bgyi zhus pa de nas bstan pa yun ring
NK068(nyu)001:12464: du gnas pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen
NK068(nyu)001:12466: de rnams kyi lag tu dbang rtags su lcags kyi
NK068(nyu)001:12467: rdo rje rtse gsum pa re byin nas rdo rje
NK068(nyu)001:12468: mii'i srin mo la sogs pa rang rang dang mthun
NK068(nyu)001:12469: pa'i ming gis dbang bskur te dkyil 'khor chen po'i
NK068(nyu)001:12470: khyams kyi phyi khyams la bkod do //
NK068(nyu)001:12471: de ltar yang ji skad du /
NK068(nyu)001:12472: dbus la 'tshal ba'i skal ba med //
NK068(nyu)001:12473: dkyil 'khor mtha' la nged rnams zhog /
NK068(nyu)001:12474: phud pa dbang ba'i skal ba med //
NK068(nyu)001:12475: lhag ma'i zhal chab bdag la zhu //
NK068(nyu)001:12479: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis su yod pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:12480: 'dis khro bo rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:12481: dkyil 'khor gyi sprin rnam par spros pa'i le'u ste
NK068(nyu)001:12483: da ni le'u bcu drug pa 'chad par byed pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:12484: chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na /
NK068(nyu)001:12485: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12486: snang ba bzhi las lam snang ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12487: lam mtha' grol gnyis las grol lam ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12488: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12489: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12490: 'bring gi chos lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12491: de la bcu las khro bo gsung gi dkyil 'khor ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12497: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK068(nyu)001:12498: de ltar ston pa'i le'u 'di la gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12504: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas gsung
NK068(nyu)001:12505: sngags kyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das
NK068(nyu)001:12506: dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs
NK068(nyu)001:12507: chen po sngar bstan pa 'di dag gsung sngags kyi
NK068(nyu)001:12508: dam tshig gis 'grub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:12509: de bzhin gshegs pa khro bo khrag 'thung chen po
NK068(nyu)001:12510: rigs lnga btsun mo dang bcas pa'i tshogs de dag
NK068(nyu)001:12511: gi sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:12512: rdo rje'i bdag nyid rang byung gi ye shes rang
NK068(nyu)001:12513: shar ba'i sngags kyi nga ro rngams pa las lhag
NK068(nyu)001:12514: ting gsung gi dkyil 'khor gyi gsang sngags 'di dag
NK068(nyu)001:12515: phyung ngo // gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:12519: gsung gi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs 'dir mngon par rtogs
NK068(nyu)001:12520: pa'i go rim gyi sdebs ma shes na bdud rtsi
NK068(nyu)001:12521: ro nyams lta bu'i bshad pa'i skyon yod pas /
NK068(nyu)001:12522: khro bo'i phrin las sgom rim gyi sdebs cung zad brjod par bya ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12525: rjes kyi rim pa dang gsum gyi sngon 'gro ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12526: mchod bsham gzhung bzhin byas la /
NK068(nyu)001:12532: mchod pa byin gyis brlab bo //
NK068(nyu)001:12533: de rnams las khyad par mtshams gcod la khro bcu rol pa mdzad do //
NK068(nyu)001:12534: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis las /
NK068(nyu)001:12535: dang po khyad par gyi sbyor ba sems bskyed pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12536: 'dzin pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal zhing //
NK068(nyu)001:12537: zhes sogs ting nge 'dzin gyi dgos ched bstan pa'i sgo nas so //
NK068(nyu)001:12538: gnyis pa ting 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos la gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12539: ting 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12540: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12541: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK068(nyu)001:12543: sgrubs thabs ltar de ting dang kun snang sngoon du 'gro bas /
NK068(nyu)001:12544: rgyu ting rang rig h+aum las cho ga gsum gyis
NK068(nyu)001:12545: rgyu'i he ru ka smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba
NK068(nyu)001:12547: rgyu'i he ru ka'i thugs ka nas sa bon spros
NK068(nyu)001:12548: te gzhi dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor gzhal yas khang
NK068(nyu)001:12549: gdan dang bcas pa bsgom la /
NK068(nyu)001:12550: le'u bcu bdun pa ltar tshig gis gsal gdab /
NK068(nyu)001:12551: de nas bdag nyid ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:12552: phyir bdag gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya
NK068(nyu)001:12553: ba bdag sras kyi cho ga ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12554: le'u bco lnga pa ltar ngo mtshar tshogs kyi lha sum cu bskyed /
NK068(nyu)001:12555: rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:12556: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya ba
NK068(nyu)001:12557: gzhan sras kyi cho ga ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12558: bdag gtso bo'i thugs ka nas thon te bskul bas /
NK068(nyu)001:12559: lha tshogs rnams las thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:12560: 'od zer spros pas bdag gi lus rtog sbyangs te
NK068(nyu)001:12561: 'od kyi gong bur gyur pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:12562: slar yang rdo rje gsum gyi 'od zer bstims pas
NK068(nyu)001:12563: yi ge 'bru gsum du gyur pa rim bzhin h+aum
NK068(nyu)001:12564: la bsdus pa de nyid zla ba la gnas pa
NK068(nyu)001:12566: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la g.yas su bskor nas gtso bo'i thugs kar thim /
NK068(nyu)001:12567: byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba sku'i dbyibs brgyud
NK068(nyu)001:12568: yum gyi mkhar son pa'i rkyen gyis gtso bo yab
NK068(nyu)001:12569: yum yang bde ba chen po'i ngo bor zhu zhing
NK068(nyu)001:12570: / h'u ha he phata ces pas 'khor rnams kyang
NK068(nyu)001:12571: dbus kyi thig ler bsdus nas 'od kyi gong bur
NK068(nyu)001:12572: bsam pa ni bdag don chos sku'i ting nge 'dzin
NK068(nyu)001:12573: gyis snang ba'i zhen pa sbyong ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12574: de nas h'u h'u zhes sgra gdangs yid la dran
NK068(nyu)001:12575: pa tsam gyis 'od phung de h'u yig zung du
NK068(nyu)001:12576: gyur pa las cho ga gsum gyis gtso bo badz+ra
NK068(nyu)001:12577: he ru ka yab yum du bskyed nas dbang bskur
NK068(nyu)001:12579: de nas mkha' gsang brlab pa sogs byas te yum
NK068(nyu)001:12580: gyi mkhar byang chub sems kyi lha'i sa bon yig
NK068(nyu)001:12581: 'bru'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa le'u 'dir bshad pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:12582: sngags kyis bskyed nas ngo mtshar tshogs kyi lha sum
NK068(nyu)001:12583: cu yum gyi mkha' las phata dzahzhesa pa'i phyir bton
NK068(nyu)001:12584: la / spro bsdus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs
NK068(nyu)001:12585: te gtso bo rang la bstim zhing 'khor rnams so
NK068(nyu)001:12587: dbang mo nyer brgyad po gtso bo'i thugs ka nas
NK068(nyu)001:12588: b+h+yo nyer brgyad so so'i gnas su spros pa las
NK068(nyu)001:12589: bskyed sngags kyis khrag khyams su bskyed cing le'u bcu
NK068(nyu)001:12590: bdun pa bzhin du tshig gis gsal gdab pa rnams
NK068(nyu)001:12591: ni gzhan don gzugs sku'i ting nge 'dzin gyis stong
NK068(nyu)001:12593: gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12594: spyan drang ba nas brtsams te 'dzab bzlas pa'i bar sa bcad drug dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12595: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la'ang /
NK068(nyu)001:12602: spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa rnams sgrub thabs ltar shes par bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12604: gsung gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:12605: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12606: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba sogs las kyi rim pa'i sngags so //
NK068(nyu)001:12608: rigs lnga yab yum bcu'i dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12609: khro mo nyi shu'i rtsa bskyed las sngags dang bcas pas /
NK068(nyu)001:12610: dbang mo rnams kyi rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK068(nyu)001:12613: sngar gyi dpe rgyun rnams su bud+d+ha he ru ka'i sngags thog mar 'byung yang /
NK068(nyu)001:12614: rgya dper badz+ra he ru ka nyid dang por yod
NK068(nyu)001:12615: ces gsungs shing thar lo'i 'gyur du'ang de ltar 'byung
NK068(nyu)001:12617: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rnam snang yin la /
NK068(nyu)001:12618: khro bo ni bud+d+ha he ru ka yin te /
NK068(nyu)001:12620: dbus kyi pho brang snying po la //
NK068(nyu)001:12621: rnam par snang mdzad phyag rgya che //
NK068(nyu)001:12622: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK068(nyu)001:12624: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo la mtshan du btags pa
NK068(nyu)001:12625: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes bya
NK068(nyu)001:12627: yang rdo rje sems dpa' gtso bo yin par ma grub ce na /
NK068(nyu)001:12630: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil nyid de //
NK068(nyu)001:12631: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK068(nyu)001:12633: yang zhi ba rnams thugs kyis 'dul ba'i phyir thugs rdo rje'i rigs gtso bor byung la /
NK068(nyu)001:12634: khro bo rnams sku yis 'dul ba'i phyir sku bud+d+ha he ru ka gtso bor byung ngo zer na /
NK068(nyu)001:12636: zhi ba gang yin pa khro bor gnas gyur pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:12637: 'og nas badz+ra he ru ka len cing gtso bor mdzad do //
NK068(nyu)001:12638: le'u bcu bdun pa'i gdan dang sku mdog la sogs pa'ang des shes par bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12639: lung gi shes byed kyang yod de /
NK068(nyu)001:12641: rgyud 'khrugs pa tshig sbas pa'i dbang du'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12643: de la sngags kyi 'go 'dren rnams ni ye shes
NK068(nyu)001:12644: lnga'i rdo rje gsum gyi bdag nyid rab sngags kyi
NK068(nyu)001:12645: sa bon no // badz+ra rdo rje /
NK068(nyu)001:12646: sarba ta th+aa ga ta de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad /
NK068(nyu)001:12650: yab lnga'i rigs so so'i mtshan /
NK068(nyu)001:12651: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka zhes pa ni spyi'i mtshan sngags bod pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12654: he ni he la ste spyod cing rtsen pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12655: ru ni ru d+hi ra ste khrag /
NK068(nyu)001:12656: ka ni bdag po'i sgra ste khrag la rol pa'i don gyi khrag 'thung ngo //
NK068(nyu)001:12657: de dag ni snying po bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK068(nyu)001:12658: ma h+aa tsan+da sogs ni las la bskul ba'i sngags te /
NK068(nyu)001:12659: ma h+aa tsan+da ni gtum po chen po /
NK068(nyu)001:12660: sarba dush+ta ni gdug pa can thams cad /
NK068(nyu)001:12661: an+ta ka ni mthar byed pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12665: h+aum gsum gyi dang po rtsa ba'i sa bon /
NK068(nyu)001:12666: gnyis pa thugs bskul ba'i sa bon /
NK068(nyu)001:12667: gsum pa ni bsdigs par mdzod /
NK068(nyu)001:12668: phata ni bkas par gyis zhes las la bskul ba'i sngags te /
NK068(nyu)001:12669: rab sngags rdo rje sogs rigs gang yin gyi dpal khrag 'thung chen po zhes bos nas /
NK068(nyu)001:12670: gtum po chen po gdug pa can thams cad mthar
NK068(nyu)001:12671: byed pas bsnun cig bsreg cig tshos shig bsdigs shig
NK068(nyu)001:12674: badz+ra sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na pad+ma rnams sngar ltar dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12675: sarba a mo g+ha thams cad don yod pa ste rigs kyi mtshan no //
NK068(nyu)001:12676: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai rnams ni khro mo dbang phyug ma chen mo //
NK068(nyu)001:12677: thog mtha'i dang phata sngar bzhin /
NK068(nyu)001:12679: khyad par du d+ha ra 'chang ba /
NK068(nyu)001:12681: sarba dush+tana gdug pa can thams cad la /
NK068(nyu)001:12682: ma h+aa s+aur+ya nyi ma chen mo /
NK068(nyu)001:12684: h+r+ai shu ta sa ma ta kun tu rgod pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12687: de ltar nyams len gyi skabs su yab yum gyi sngags sdebs nas shes par bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12694: ni rab sngags ye shes lnga dang ldan pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12695: badz+ra rnams ni rdo rje ste dbang rtags su rdo rje rtse lnga pas dbu brgyan par mtshon pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12696: mjug gi ha brgyad ni rtsa ba'i sa bon /
NK068(nyu)001:12697: bye brag goo r+ai dkar mo'am mdzod ldan ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12698: tsoo r+ai chom rkun mo'am rkun mo /
NK068(nyu)001:12699: pra mo he rab rmongs ma'am rmongs mo /
NK068(nyu)001:12700: bee ta l+ai ni ro langs ma'am thal byed ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12703: g+hasma r+ai sme sha can nam dred mo /
NK068(nyu)001:12704: sme sha ni dur khrod ma'am ma tshogs ma'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12708: mjug gi he brgyad rtsa ba'i sa bon /
NK068(nyu)001:12709: sed+ha mu kh+ai seng gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12710: b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai stag gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12711: sh+ri g+aa la mu kh+ai wa gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12712: shwa na mu kh+ai khyi gdong ma'am spyang gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12713: gri d+ha mu kh+ai bya rgod gdong ma'am bzhad gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12714: kang+ka mu kh+ai kang+ka'i gdong ma'am dur bya'i gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12715: k+aa ka mu kh+ai khwa gdong ma'am bya rog gdong ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12716: u l+au ka mu kh+ai 'ug gdong ma'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12720: +aar+ya te dza te nga 'phags ma sring 'gro ma'am ring 'gro ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12721: a m+au khe gdong mo'am don yod ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12723: b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu thal bar byed ma /
NK068(nyu)001:12724: mjug gi dzahh+aum bam hohbazhi ni sa bon no //
NK068(nyu)001:12725: gsum pa dbang mo'i rtsa sngags ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12726: b+h+yo drug tshan bzhi dang bzhi tshan gcig ste nyer
NK068(nyu)001:12727: brgyad ni ma mo'i tshogs kyi don dang snying po'ang
NK068(nyu)001:12728: yin la / bod pa dang bskul ba'ang yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:12730: ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo sogs bshad rgyud me long las gsungs pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12731: dbang mo rnams kha cig gis /
NK068(nyu)001:12733: b+h+yo ni las byed ma mo ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12734: las kyi mkha' 'gror thig ler chags //
NK068(nyu)001:12735: zhes pas mkha' nas 'don par mngon zer kyang /
NK068(nyu)001:12736: 'di ni sras ma yin te byi mo yin pa'i phyir /
NK068(nyu)001:12737: mkha' las mi 'don te thugs ka nas b+h+yo las chu bur ltar bskyed par 'dod do //
NK068(nyu)001:12738: gnyis pa las kyi rim pa'i sngags la gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12740: me tog 'dor zhing dngos grub bskul ba'i tshig sngags /
NK068(nyu)001:12741: drin lan du mchod cing brtan pa'i sngags so //
NK068(nyu)001:12743: ru lu ru lu h+aum zhes pa snyan gsan dbab pa'i sngags te /
NK068(nyu)001:12744: spyir ru dza'i sgra las 'jigs par gyis /
NK068(nyu)001:12747: sngags kyi lha bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jig cing chod
NK068(nyu)001:12748: la bsdigs par mdzod ces pas gdul bya gdug pa
NK068(nyu)001:12749: can gyi ngor chos kyi sku las 'jigs byed chen
NK068(nyu)001:12750: por bzhengs par mdzod ces bskul ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12751: yang na ru lu zhes pa'i spyir chos sku bye
NK068(nyu)001:12752: brag dkyil 'khor lha las khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab
NK068(nyu)001:12753: yum dang / ru lu zhes pas longs sku'am gnas yul sgo ma dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12754: ru lu zhes pas sprul sku'am dbang mo ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12755: de dag la snyan gsan phab pas chos sku'i ngang
NK068(nyu)001:12756: las ma g.yos bzhin du gzugs skur bzhengs nas ting
NK068(nyu)001:12757: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ci 'dra ba'i rnam par
NK068(nyu)001:12758: bzhengs shig pa'o // sngags 'di sngon las kyi srin
NK068(nyu)001:12759: po'i dam tshig gi gdug pa'i glu dpal chen po'i
NK068(nyu)001:12761: de nas h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa pa ni spyan drang ba'i sngags te /
NK068(nyu)001:12762: e h+ye hi tshur spyon tshur spyon /
NK068(nyu)001:12764: dzahh+aum bam hohtshad med bzhis 'gro don la bskul ba'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12765: ram ni dam ye gnyis med me ri 'dabs 'byor tsam du bzhugs pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12766: de ltar dbab drangs kyi sngags la dgos pa ci yod ce na /
NK068(nyu)001:12767: bi shwa mi tra'i gzhung las /
NK068(nyu)001:12768: mnyes dka' ma yin bkur nas phyir //
NK068(nyu)001:12769: 'jig rten dbang po'i chos lugs kyis //
NK068(nyu)001:12771: dper na 'jig rten gyi rgyal po lta bu spyan
NK068(nyu)001:12772: 'dren pa la snyan gsan dbab pa la sogs tshul
NK068(nyu)001:12773: dang mthun par bya dgos te /
NK068(nyu)001:12774: de ltar ma byas na ko long du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK068(nyu)001:12775: de bzhin du 'dir ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor ni
NK068(nyu)001:12776: de ltar mnyes par dka' ba ste ko long can
NK068(nyu)001:12777: ma yin yang / dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gyis
NK068(nyu)001:12778: sri zhu gus pa'i sgo nas tshul mthun zhing ye
NK068(nyu)001:12779: shes kyi dkyil 'khor bkur nas gnas su bya ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:12780: phyir snyan gsan phab nas spyan drangs pa yin no
NK068(nyu)001:12781: ma yin yang / // gnyis pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12782: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum ni me tog 'dor ba ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12784: badz+ra kro d+ha rdo rje khro bo /
NK068(nyu)001:12787: khro la sogs ni dngos grub bskul ba ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12788: +amo ni ye shes lnga ldan glu'i 'go 'dren no //
NK068(nyu)001:12789: rang bzhin gyis khro la mdzad pa las kyi phyag
NK068(nyu)001:12790: rgya'i skur snang nas thugs rje khros pa'i tshul bstan
NK068(nyu)001:12791: pas dregs pa can gdug pa'i tshogs kyi gdul bya
NK068(nyu)001:12792: rnams kyi rgyud zhi bar mdzad pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12793: de yang thugs rje ngang gis khro bor sprul pa
NK068(nyu)001:12794: ni 'phro ba'i dpal chen po rab tu rngams pa'i
NK068(nyu)001:12795: tshogs chen po'o // khro bo khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i
NK068(nyu)001:12796: dkyil 'khor gyi byin rlabs sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK068(nyu)001:12797: phrin las gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas ngo
NK068(nyu)001:12798: mtshar rmad po che de nyid dus da lta nyid
NK068(nyu)001:12799: du ni bdag la stsol cig ces gsol ba btab
NK068(nyu)001:12800: tshogs chen po'o // nas / slar yang thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12801: badz+ra kro d+ha gsum ni sngar ltar dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12802: sa ma ya dam tshig gam dus la /
NK068(nyu)001:12803: s+t+wam khyod ces bod pa'am bab bo //
NK068(nyu)001:12805: hohmanyesa par mdzod ces pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12806: mchog ster rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig khyod /
NK068(nyu)001:12808: dam tshig gis dgyes par mdzod ces pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12811: a ba b+h+ram sha zur chag pa'i skad yin ces rong zom chos kyi bzang pos gsungs /
NK068(nyu)001:12812: de la a li ni chang ste btung ba /
NK068(nyu)001:12813: u li ni sha ste bza' ba /
NK068(nyu)001:12814: t+aa li t+aa b+aa li 'bru 'bras sogs dam tshig gi rdzas sna tshogs /
NK068(nyu)001:12815: dash+ta zhal mche ba bgrad pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12819: rdo rje khro bo mche ba bgrad pa'i zhal du stob bo //
NK068(nyu)001:12820: zhes khro bo yab yum gyi tshogs dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12824: 'khor gyi rnal 'byor ma rnams la stob pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12825: h+aum ha he phata ni dam ye gnyis med du gyur nas gsal zhing brtan par byas pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12826: de yang lha la lha thim /
NK068(nyu)001:12827: gzhal yas khang la gzhal yas khang thim /
NK068(nyu)001:12828: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang dam tshig gi dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:12829: 'khor gnyis chu dang 'o ma 'drees pa bzhin dbyer
NK068(nyu)001:12830: med du gyur par bsam mo //
NK068(nyu)001:12833: gsung gi dkyil 'khor gyi don de skad ces brjod
NK068(nyu)001:12834: pa'i byin rlabs kyis 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i
NK068(nyu)001:12835: 'gro ba thams cad kyi lus snang ba'i rtog tshogs
NK068(nyu)001:12836: thams cad tshig / ngag grags pa'i rtog tshogs rab tu tshig /
NK068(nyu)001:12837: sems sgrib pa'i rtog tshogs thams cad kun tu tshig go //
NK068(nyu)001:12838: de ltar tshig pas snang ba thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'bar /
NK068(nyu)001:12839: grags pa thams cad sngags kyi dkyil 'khor du rab tu 'bar /
NK068(nyu)001:12840: dran rig thams cad thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du kun tu 'bar ro //
NK068(nyu)001:12841: de'i tshe nam mkhas gar khyab thams cad du 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs kyi skus gang /
NK068(nyu)001:12842: gsung gis khyab par rab tu gang /
NK068(nyu)001:12843: thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyis kun tu khyab cing gang bar gyur to //
NK068(nyu)001:12844: mdor na snang grags rig gsum gyi dkyil 'khor thams
NK068(nyu)001:12845: cad dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs dang dbyer med
NK068(nyu)001:12846: ro gcig tu gyur pa'i don no //
NK068(nyu)001:12849: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis su yod pa las /
NK068(nyu)001:12850: 'dis le'u bco lnga pa'i skabs su bshad pa'i khro
NK068(nyu)001:12851: bo chen po'i gsung sngags kyi dkyil 'khor rtsa ba
NK068(nyu)001:12852: bskyed pa las rim gyi sngags sogs spros pa'i le'u
NK068(nyu)001:12855: // da ni le'u bcu bdun pa 'chad par byed pa la /
NK068(nyu)001:12856: chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na /
NK068(nyu)001:12857: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12858: thabs grol gnyis las grol lam ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12859: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12860: snang ba bzhi las lam snang ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12861: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12862: 'bring gi chos lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12863: de la bcu las khro bo'i sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12865: lha bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin ston /
NK068(nyu)001:12869: spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK068(nyu)001:12870: de ltar ston pa'i le'u 'di la gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12876: gsung gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas lhag pa
NK068(nyu)001:12877: sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir bcom
NK068(nyu)001:12878: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i sprin gsang
NK068(nyu)001:12879: sngags dang bcas pa de dag gis bskyed pa'i dkyil
NK068(nyu)001:12880: 'khor gyi rnam pa gsal bar bstan pa'i phyir ched
NK068(nyu)001:12881: du brjod pa 'di dag brjod do //
NK068(nyu)001:12882: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:12889: ngo bo rgyan dang bcas pa dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12892: 'bar ba'i 'khor lo sogs rkang pa drug ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12893: 'og gzhi tshad med pa'i 'khor lo'i lte ba la
NK068(nyu)001:12894: rdzogs pa'i ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin thod
NK068(nyu)001:12895: pa 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus su ye
NK068(nyu)001:12896: shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su 'khor lo rtsibs
NK068(nyu)001:12897: bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12898: de'i phyir bden pa bzhi mtshon pa'i gru chad bzhis rnam par brgyan cing /
NK068(nyu)001:12899: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i phyir dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12900: rnam thar bzhi dang ldan pa'i sgo bzhi sgo khyud dang ldan pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12901: bden gnyis mtshon pa'i 'bar ba'i bar khyams nang ma gser khyams dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12902: phyi ma khrag khyams gnyis kyis mdzes shing /
NK068(nyu)001:12903: thod pa skam rlon rnying gsum gyi rtsig pa phyi ma rim pa lnga dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12905: thams cad kyang rak+tasa spyin thabs su sbyar zhing gnam lcags kyi gzer bu'i btab pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12906: rtsig steng thod pa sna tshogs kyi pha gu 'phyar
NK068(nyu)001:12907: ba las rgyu ma dang snying gi mgul 'khor dang
NK068(nyu)001:12908: / bre phul gyi snam bur sbrul sbram dang thod phreng gi d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa /
NK068(nyu)001:12911: rim pa gnyis ka'i rtsig pa'i 'gram du 'dod yon gyi snam bu dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12912: sgo phyi ma la rgyu 'bras kyi rta babs sogs 'jigs pa'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis bkra ba /
NK068(nyu)001:12913: steng zhing lpags kyi thog phubs nyi ma dang zla
NK068(nyu)001:12914: ba'i mthong dkar dang bcas pa'i dbus phyur bu lha
NK068(nyu)001:12915: chen gyi thod pas phub pa'i rtse mor tsit+ta'i tog
NK068(nyu)001:12916: gis brjid pa / phyi rol du r+au tra longs
NK068(nyu)001:12917: spyod dang bcas pa dbyings su bsgral ba'i dur khrod
NK068(nyu)001:12918: brgyad kyis yongs su bskor zhing /
NK068(nyu)001:12919: 'bar ba'i me dpung me'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba'i klong
NK068(nyu)001:12920: nas khro chung mang po 'phro zhing 'khrugs pas mdzes
NK068(nyu)001:12922: khyu mchog sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:12923: dbus kyi lte ba dang rtsibs bzhir yon tan gyi
NK068(nyu)001:12924: che ba rang snang gi gdan pad+ma zla nyi brtsegs
NK068(nyu)001:12925: pa'i steng du / gti mug gnas su dag pa'i rtags su shar rtsibs la khyu mchog dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12926: nga rgyal dag pa lhor ma he dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12927: 'dod chags dag pa nub tu gzig dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12928: phrag dog dag pa byang du stag dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12929: zhe sdang dag pa dbus su gtum po dom rnams
NK068(nyu)001:12930: zung gis sbar ba'i steng phrin las nan tur du
NK068(nyu)001:12931: bstan pa'i phyir dregs pa zil gnon gyi gdan dbus
NK068(nyu)001:12932: su dbang phyug dang lha chen po drag po la
NK068(nyu)001:12933: sogs pas shar du dri za /
NK068(nyu)001:12936: byang du gnod sbyin rnams pho mo kha sbubs gan
NK068(nyu)001:12937: rkyal du bsnol ba'i sog sbrag dang nu sbrag nas
NK068(nyu)001:12938: las la nan tur du brtan pa'i phyir bzung ba'o
NK068(nyu)001:12939: // 'di la khyu mchog ces pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12941: gdan mchog gdul dka' mi 'jigs khyu mchog dang //
NK068(nyu)001:12944: mi 'jigs bzhi ldan khyu mchog ste //
NK068(nyu)001:12945: zhes pas seng ge la bshad do //
NK068(nyu)001:12947: khyu mchog glang po che'i gnas su bca' zhes pas glang po cher bshad do //
NK068(nyu)001:12948: snga rabs pa rnams kyis de gnyis rol pa las byung bar bzhed do //
NK068(nyu)001:12949: de ltar gdan 'di rnams mngon rtogs las /
NK068(nyu)001:12950: lha chen po rnams kyis bzhon pa phrogs pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12952: dpa' rtags kyi gdan du gsal lo //
NK068(nyu)001:12953: 'khor gyi gnas yul sgo skyong rnams la nyi ma dang zhing rlon gyi gdan /
NK068(nyu)001:12954: dbang mo rnams la zhing skam po'i gdan re re'o //
NK068(nyu)001:12955: gnyis pa brten pa lha la gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:12956: gtso bo rigs lnga'i bzhugs tshul dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12965: smug nag sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK068(nyu)001:12966: de yang drag po'i phrin las kyi nang nas zhi
NK068(nyu)001:12967: ba'i las mdzad pa'i rtags su shar du bud+d+ha he
NK068(nyu)001:12968: ru ka'i sku mdog smug nag /
NK068(nyu)001:12969: drag po'i phrin las kho na mdzad pa'i rtags su
NK068(nyu)001:12970: dbus kyi gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka'i sku mdog
NK068(nyu)001:12971: sngo nag / drag po'i phrin las kyi cha las
NK068(nyu)001:12972: rgyas pa'i las mdzad pa'i rtags su lhor rat+na he
NK068(nyu)001:12974: drag po'i phrin las kyi cha las dbang gi phrin
NK068(nyu)001:12975: las mdzad pa'i rtags su nub tu pad+ma he ru
NK068(nyu)001:12976: ka dmar nag / drag po'i phrin las kyi cha
NK068(nyu)001:12977: las las sna tshogs mdzad pa'i rtags su byang du
NK068(nyu)001:12978: karma he ru ka ljang nag ste sku mdog rtsa
NK068(nyu)001:12980: de dag kyang rigs mi 'gyur zhing las bzhi'i phrin
NK068(nyu)001:12981: las kyi gzhi dang mthar phyin pa drag pos mdzad
NK068(nyu)001:12982: pa'i phyir thams cad la nag po'i sgras smros pa'o
NK068(nyu)001:12983: // g.yas zhal ni rat+na he ru ka'i sngon po dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12985: g.yon zhal ni bud+d+ha dang pad+ma gnyis ser po dang /
NK068(nyu)001:12987: khro bo de dag thams cad kyang sku che zhing
NK068(nyu)001:12988: yan lag rags pas gdug pa can gyi ngor shin
NK068(nyu)001:12992: thams cad kyang rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dbu gsum /
NK068(nyu)001:12993: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug /
NK068(nyu)001:12994: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags
NK068(nyu)001:12995: su zhabs bzhi g.yas brkyang ba'i dor stabs su bgrad
NK068(nyu)001:12996: pa'o // gzhan yang nyi zla bye ba'i 'od zer
NK068(nyu)001:12997: dus gcig la 'phro ba lta bus brjid cing 'od
NK068(nyu)001:12998: pa'o // zer 'bar ba'o // gsum pa ni /
NK068(nyu)001:12999: ko rlon sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK068(nyu)001:13000: 'bar ba chen po khro bo'i lha tshogs de dag kyang dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad dang /
NK068(nyu)001:13001: dpal gyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK068(nyu)001:13002: dang po la bgo ba'i gos gsum /
NK068(nyu)001:13004: byug pa'i rdzas gsum dang brgyad las /
NK068(nyu)001:13005: dang po bgo ba'i gos gsum ni /
NK068(nyu)001:13006: bgo ba ko rlon gyi gos ni sna tshogs pa gyon pa ste /
NK068(nyu)001:13007: stobs bcus gti mug bcom pa'i brdar khyab pa thugs
NK068(nyu)001:13008: rje'i gos sam 'dul stobs theg pa'i rgyan glang chen
NK068(nyu)001:13010: byang chub sems kyis 'dod chags bcom pa'i brdar thabs
NK068(nyu)001:13011: mkhas phrin las kyi gos sam tshul khrims gos kyi
NK068(nyu)001:13012: rgyan zhing lpags kyi stod g.yogs shing /
NK068(nyu)001:13013: dpa' brtul drag po'i las kyis zhe sdang bcom pa'i
